{"type":"message","id":"e5014a6a","parentId":"75ab32f2","timestamp":"2026-04-13T04:18:12.580Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"Now I have a clear picture. Let me verify the actual service statuses:\n\n1. **3103 (v8 scorer)**: Running (node, pid 580)\n2. **3104 (scene-classifier)**: Running (pt_main_thread, pid 442) \n3. **3102 (openclaw-gateway)**: Running (openclaw-gateway, pid 578)\n4. **3101 (context-api)**: Running (node, pid 434)\n5. **openclaw-router**: Directory exists but not running as a service\n\nThe方案 says:\n- openclaw-router(3102) ← 死了(dotenv+3108) - but 3102 is the gateway port, not the router\n\n\n- ws-proxy points to 3108 which is wrong (should be 3102)\n- scene-classifier at 3104 is actually running, not 500 error\n\nLet me verify these services actually respond and check what's happening with the ws-proxy configuration.","thinkingSignature":"964e89888864648d545c17e1ba4a6997b47b3dfe3460a44e0c837227ce73a3a5"},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_5ab409fe4f364a8892d69524","name":"exec","arguments":{"command":"curl -s --max-time 3 http://localhost:3104/classify -X POST -H \"Content-Type: application/json\" -d '{\"text\":\"测试\"}' 2>&1 | head -20"}}],"api":"anthropic-messages","provider":"minimax","model":"MiniMax-M2.7","usage":{"input":381,"output":269,"cacheRead":28544,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":29194,"cost":{"input":0.0001143,"output":0.0003228,"cacheRead":0.0017126399999999999,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0.00214974}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1776053885075,"responseId":"062ba17c938ceae5c2a8aec9b3d70bf9"}}
