{"type":"message","id":"ed30a44c","parentId":"9a25b186","timestamp":"2026-04-13T04:23:05.135Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"The user wants me to think about what I found in the comprehensive framework check. Let me analyze the key issues and think through the root causes and connections.\n\nKey findings:\n1. 3104 scene-classifier - two instances competing for the same port, running on python3.8 (pid 442) but degraded to rule-based fallback\n2. openclaw-router - not running due to missing dotenv\n3. v8 scorer (3103) - running fine\n4. Gateway (3102) - healthy\n5. context-api (3101) - running but not connected to anything\n6. Cron jobs - wiki-auto-learn, memory-keeper, memory-maintain all not configured\n\n\n7. bootstrap and session-summary - not verified\n\nThe core problem is that these services were built across different development phases with overlapping functionality but no unified management. To fix this properly, I need to stop the duplicate v8 instance, configure the workspace skill to run on 3104, install the missing dotenv dependency for openclaw-router, and then systematically wire up the cron jobs for memory management and wiki learning. I should also verify that bootstrap and session-summary are functioning correctly after these changes.","thinkingSignature":"f0e497b8d9ccf0adf34dd71bfc1c839d5e5dbdd5e6537982b5cf88a9f17d7363"},{"type":"text","text":"\n\n好，系统思考一下。\n\n---\n\n## 核心问题：三层系统各自为战\n\n方案里描述的状态是准确的，但有一个更深的问题没被充分点出来：\n\n**这套框架不是\"坏掉了\"，而是从来没有完全跑起来过。**\n\n---\n\n### 为什么这么说\n\n| 组件 | 什么时候坏的 | 真实原因 |\n|------|-------------|---------|\n| 3104 classifier | **从未稳定工作过** | 两个实例抢端口，sentence-transformers 从未装成功，一直 rule-based fallback |\n| openclaw-router | **从未成功启动** | dotenv 从第一天就缺，@reboot 一直失败 |\n| wiki-auto-learn | **跑过一次就停了** | 没有 cron，靠手动触发 |\n| memory-keeper | **装了但没配触发** | 同上 |\n\n这些不是\"退化\"的问题，是**初始部署就不完整**。\n\n---\n\n### 当前的真实状态\n\n```\n3103(v8 scorer)    ✅ 正常跑，没人调用（因为 3104 链断了）\n3104(classifier)   ⚠️  规则兜底跑着，embedding 模型从未真正加载\n3102(gateway)      ✅ 健康，处理实时 session\n3101(context-api)  ⚠️  活着，但没有任何服务调用它\nopenclaw-router   ❌ 从未跑成功过\ncron jobs         ❌ 全都没配\n记忆层            ❌ 全靠手动触发\n```\n\n---\n\n### 关键洞察\n\n**修 3104 和 router 不是在\"修复\"，是在\"补初始部署\"。**\n\n这意味着：\n1. 修完之后，框架不会自动变聪明——只是刚具备正常工作条件\n2. 真正让框架活起来的是 cron + 记忆层流通\n3. 方案里的 Step 4-9（cron 配置）比 Step 1-3 更关键\n\n---\n\n### 我的判断\n\n**方案优先级建议调整：**\n\n```\n第一步（今天，先补缺）：\n  ① 统一 3104 到一个实例（停 python3.8 版本）\n  ② 装 dotenv，启动 openclaw-router\n  ③ 配 3 条 cron（wiki/memory/health）\n  ④ 验证链路：curl 3104 → 看 classifier 响应\n\n第二步（明天，验证链路）：\n  ⑤ 触发 /new，验证 session-summary 生成\n  ⑥ 验证 bootstrap 读取摘要\n  ⑦ 验证 v8 scorer 被调用（看 3103 日志）\n\n第三步（本周，长期）：\n  ⑧ wiki-auto-learn --api 模式\n  ⑨ 备份 cron\n```\n\n**核心观点：方案 P0 是对的，但 P1 应该提到 P0 后面立刻做，不能等明天。**"}],"api":"anthropic-messages","provider":"minimax","model":"MiniMax-M2.7","usage":{"input":926,"output":802,"cacheRead":38464,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":40192,"cost":{"input":0.0002778,"output":0.0009624,"cacheRead":0.00230784,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0.0035480399999999997}},"stopReason":"stop","timestamp":1776054168834,"responseId":"062ba2982b2cc4a7fb434705bfd910fe"}}
