{"type":"message","id":"72eea7b7","parentId":"6baa7bfc","timestamp":"2026-04-13T04:24:00.359Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"The user wants me to give them the revised plan based on my analysis. Let me write it out clearly.","thinkingSignature":"b4ced3045f9747accd47ccdd773932e707ff219f3d984929c84426ccec8d14ee"},{"type":"text","text":"\n\n## 框架修复执行方案\n\n---\n\n### Step 1：统一 3104 实例（5分钟）\n\n**问题**：两个实例抢端口，sentence-transformers 从未装成功\n\n```bash\n# 1. 停掉 python3.8 版本（pid 442）\nkill 442\n\n# 2. 确认 workspace skill 版本可执行\ncd ~/.openclaw/workspace/skills/scene-classifier\npip install sentence-transformers 2>/dev/null || pip3 install sentence-transformers\n\n# 3. 启动 workspace 版本\nnohup python3 api_server.py > logs/api.log 2>&1 &\n\n# 4. 验证\ncurl -s -X POST http://localhost:3104/classify -H \"Content-Type: application/json\" -d '{\"text\":\"帮我写一个备份脚本\"}'\n```\n\n---\n\n### Step 2：修 openclaw-router（5分钟）\n\n```bash\ncd /home/ai/openclaw-router && npm install dotenv\n\n# 修改端口：3108 → 3102\nsed -i 's/localhost:3108/localhost:3102/g' openclaw-router.js ws-proxy.js\n\n# 启动\nnohup node openclaw-router.js > /tmp/router.log 2>&1 &\n```\n\n---\n\n### Step 3：配 cron（5分钟）\n\n```bash\n# wiki-auto-learn 每小时增量\n0 * * * * cd ~/.openclaw/workspace && python3 scripts/wiki-auto-learn.py --mode=ingest --limit=3 >> logs/wiki-ingest.log 2>&1\n\n# memory-keeper 每天4点\n0 4 * * * ~/.openclaw/workspace/scripts/memory_keeper.sh >> ~/.openclaw/workspace/logs/memory-maintain.log 2>&1\n\n# memory-maintain 每天3点\n0 3 * * * ~/.openclaw/workspace/scripts/memory_maintain.sh >> ~/.openclaw/workspace/logs/memory-maintain.log 2>&1\n\n# health-check 每5分钟（可选）\n*/5 * * * * python3 ~/.openclaw/workspace/scripts/health-check.py >> ~/.openclaw/workspace/logs/health.log 2>&1\n```\n\n---\n\n### Step 4：关掉无效天气 cron\n\n```bash\ncrontab -e\n# 删除这行：\n# 0 8 * * * /home/ai/.openclaw/workspace/scripts/weather_report.sh ...\n```\n\n---\n\n### Step 5：验证链路（2分钟）\n\n```bash\n# 3104 是否正常\ncurl -s -X POST http://localhost:3104/classify \\\n  -H \"Content-Type: application/json\" \\\n  -d '{\"text\":\"测试消息\"}'\n\n# 3103 是否被调用（发消息后检查日志）\ntail -f ~/.openclaw/v8/logs/openclaw.log\n```\n\n---\n\n## 执行顺序\n\n```\n今天（20分钟）：\n  Step 1 → Step 2 → Step 3 → Step 4 → Step 5\n\n明天（验证）：\n  发 /new，看 memory/ 有没有摘要生成\n  确认 bootstrap 读到了上轮内容\n\n本周（1小时）：\n  Step 6: wiki-auto-learn --api 模式接入 task_orchestrator\n  Step 7: git 备份 cron\n```\n\n---\n\n先从 Step 1 开始？"}],"api":"anthropic-messages","provider":"minimax","model":"MiniMax-M2.7","usage":{"input":650,"output":721,"cacheRead":39360,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":40731,"cost":{"input":0.000195,"output":0.0008652,"cacheRead":0.0023615999999999997,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0.0034218}},"stopReason":"stop","timestamp":1776054227079,"responseId":"062ba2d22e882a863efee1b08a26f866"}}
