{"type":"message","id":"0f20cb12","parentId":"8bf78870","timestamp":"2026-04-13T04:30:45.340Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"The pipeline initializes fine when called directly. The issue must be in the FastAPI app startup or request handling. Let me check if there's a startup event that fails, or if the classify endpoint itself is failing.\n\nLet me check the FastAPI app's lifespan or startup events, and whether there's an error being swallowed.\n\nActually, let me look at the workspace skill's api_server.py more carefully - it might have a different error handling path.","thinkingSignature":"da8cb4fd3299a0e6352c053cff4a58f093bbc0d23d6408a00efcd711b818b516"},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_62575d8634f94eacaba931f8","name":"exec","arguments":{"command":"cat ~/.openclaw/workspace/skills/scene-classifier/api_server.py"}}],"api":"anthropic-messages","provider":"minimax","model":"MiniMax-M2.7","usage":{"input":216,"output":127,"cacheRead":47168,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":47511,"cost":{"input":0.0000648,"output":0.0001524,"cacheRead":0.0028300799999999996,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0.0030472799999999994}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1776054640064,"responseId":"062ba47049d1057f101b2ace8fdbfcea"}}
{"type":"message","id":"287a066e","parentId":"0f20cb12","timestamp":"2026-04-13T04:30:45.435Z","message":{"role":"toolResult","toolCallId":"call_62575d8634f94eacaba931f8","toolName":"exec","content":[{"type":"text","text":"#!/usr/bin/env python3\n\"\"\"\nScene Classifier API 服务\n启动: python api_server.py\n访问: http://localhost:8080\n\"\"\"\n\nimport os\nimport sys\nos.environ['HF_ENDPOINT'] = 'https://hf-mirror.com'\n\nfrom fastapi import FastAPI, HTTPException\nfrom pydantic import BaseModel\nfrom fastapi.middleware.cors import CORSMiddleware\nimport uvicorn\n\n# 添加路径\nsys.path.insert(0, '/home/ai/.openclaw/workspace/skills/scene-classifier')\n\nfrom pipeline.orchestrator import PipelineOrchestrator\nfrom feedback.collector import FeedbackCollector\n\napp = FastAPI(title=\"Scene Classifier API\", version=\"2.0\")\n\n# CORS 支持\napp.add_middleware(\n    CORSMiddleware,\n    allow_origins=[\"*\"],\n    allow_credentials=True,\n    allow_methods=[\"*\"],\n    allow_headers=[\"*\"],\n)\n\n# 初始化\ntry:\n    pipeline = PipelineOrchestrator()\n    feedback = FeedbackCollector()\n    print(\"Pipeline initialized\")\nexcept Exception as e:\n    pipeline = None\n    print(f\"Pipeline init failed: {e}\")\n\n# 请求模型\nclass ClassifyRequest(BaseModel):\n    text: str\n    context: dict = {}\n\nclass FeedbackRequest(BaseModel):\n    text: str\n    predicted_label: str\n    feedback_type: str\n    correct_label: str = None\n\n@app.get(\"/\")\ndef root():\n    return {\n        \"name\": \"Scene Classifier API\",\n        \"version\": \"2.0\",\n        \"endpoints\": {\n            \"classify\": \"/classify (POST)\",\n            \"feedback\": \"/feedback (POST)\",\n            \"stats\": \"/stats (GET)\",\n        }\n    }\n\n@app.get(\"/health\")\ndef health():\n    return {\"status\": \"ok\", \"pipeline_loaded\": pipeline is not None}\n\n@app.post(\"/classify\")\ndef classify(req: ClassifyRequest):\n    if not pipeline:\n        raise HTTPException(status_code=500, detail=\"Pipeline not initialized\")\n    \n    result = pipeline.process(req.text, req.context)\n    return result\n\n@app.post(\"/feedback\")\ndef submit_feedback(req: FeedbackRequest):\n    if not feedback:\n        raise HTTPException(status_code=500, detail=\"Feedback not initialized\")\n    \n    return {\"status\": \"recorded\"}\n\n@app.get(\"/stats\")\ndef get_stats():\n    return {\"message\": \"Check logs/meta_events.jsonl\"}\n\nif __name__ == \"__main__\":\n    print(\"Scene Classifier API v2.0 starting on port 8080...\")\n    uvicorn.run(app, host=\"0.0.0.0\", port=8080)"}],"details":{"status":"completed","exitCode":0,"durationMs":56,"aggregated":"#!/usr/bin/env python3\n\"\"\"\nScene Classifier API 服务\n启动: python api_server.py\n访问: http://localhost:8080\n\"\"\"\n\nimport os\nimport sys\nos.environ['HF_ENDPOINT'] = 'https://hf-mirror.com'\n\nfrom fastapi import FastAPI, HTTPException\nfrom pydantic import BaseModel\nfrom fastapi.middleware.cors import CORSMiddleware\nimport uvicorn\n\n# 添加路径\nsys.path.insert(0, '/home/ai/.openclaw/workspace/skills/scene-classifier')\n\nfrom pipeline.orchestrator import PipelineOrchestrator\nfrom feedback.collector import FeedbackCollector\n\napp = FastAPI(title=\"Scene Classifier API\", version=\"2.0\")\n\n# CORS 支持\napp.add_middleware(\n    CORSMiddleware,\n    allow_origins=[\"*\"],\n    allow_credentials=True,\n    allow_methods=[\"*\"],\n    allow_headers=[\"*\"],\n)\n\n# 初始化\ntry:\n    pipeline = PipelineOrchestrator()\n    feedback = FeedbackCollector()\n    print(\"Pipeline initialized\")\nexcept Exception as e:\n    pipeline = None\n    print(f\"Pipeline init failed: {e}\")\n\n# 请求模型\nclass ClassifyRequest(BaseModel):\n    text: str\n    context: dict = {}\n\nclass FeedbackRequest(BaseModel):\n    text: str\n    predicted_label: str\n    feedback_type: str\n    correct_label: str = None\n\n@app.get(\"/\")\ndef root():\n    return {\n        \"name\": \"Scene Classifier API\",\n        \"version\": \"2.0\",\n        \"endpoints\": {\n            \"classify\": \"/classify (POST)\",\n            \"feedback\": \"/feedback (POST)\",\n            \"stats\": \"/stats (GET)\",\n        }\n    }\n\n@app.get(\"/health\")\ndef health():\n    return {\"status\": \"ok\", \"pipeline_loaded\": pipeline is not None}\n\n@app.post(\"/classify\")\ndef classify(req: ClassifyRequest):\n    if not pipeline:\n        raise HTTPException(status_code=500, detail=\"Pipeline not initialized\")\n    \n    result = pipeline.process(req.text, req.context)\n    return result\n\n@app.post(\"/feedback\")\ndef submit_feedback(req: FeedbackRequest):\n    if not feedback:\n        raise HTTPException(status_code=500, detail=\"Feedback not initialized\")\n    \n    return {\"status\": \"recorded\"}\n\n@app.get(\"/stats\")\ndef get_stats():\n    return {\"message\": \"Check logs/meta_events.jsonl\"}\n\nif __name__ == \"__main__\":\n    print(\"Scene Classifier API v2.0 starting on port 8080...\")\n    uvicorn.run(app, host=\"0.0.0.0\", port=8080)","cwd":"/home/ai/.openclaw/workspace/main"},"isError":false,"timestamp":1776054645424}}
{"type":"message","id":"bd6e5aa5","parentId":"287a066e","timestamp":"2026-04-13T04:31:00.664Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"Found it! The workspace skill's api_server.py has a bug - it's hardcoded to port 8080:\n\n```python\nif __name__ == \"__main__\":\n    print(\"Scene Classifier API v2.0 starting on port 8080...\")\n    uvicorn.run(app, host=\"0.0.0.0\", port=8080)\n```\n\nAnd the v8 version is hardcoded to port 3104. That's why:\n- v8 version抢3104 → workspace version tries 8080 → both seem to fail\n- But wait, earlier we saw the v8 version was on 3104... and returning 500\n\nWait, looking at the logs again:\n```\nINFO:     Uvicorn running on http://0.0.0.0:8080 (Press CTRL+C to quit)\n```\nThat's from the workspace version trying to run on 8080.\n\nBut we also saw:\n```\nERROR:    [Errno 98] error while attempting to bind on address ('0.0.0.0', 8080): address already in use\n```\n\nSo 8080 was already in use by something else (maybe the earlier v8 instance that started on 8080 first, then failed to bind 3104).\n\nThe current state: v8 version (11366) is on 3104 returning 500. Workspace version couldn't start because 8080 was taken.\n\nActually wait - let me re-read the log output more carefully. Earlier I saw:\n1. v8 version tried 3104, failed (EADDRINUSE)\n2. v8 version then fell back to... actually no, it still should be trying 3104\n\nThe logs showed:\n```\nERROR:    [Errno 98] error while attempting to bind on address ('0.0.0.0', 3104): address already in use\n...\nLoaded embedding classifier from /home/ai/.openclaw/workspace/skills/scene-classifier/models/scene_classifier.pkl\n\n\nPipeline initialized\nScene Classifier API v2.0 starting on port 3104...\n```\n\nSo the v8 version tried 3104 first (EADDRINUSE), then successfully loaded the model and started on 3104. But 3104 was already taken, so when I checked `lsof -i :3104`, there was a process listening. The v8 version crashed, then I killed the other process, but the v8 version is still returning 500 on 3104.\n\nSo the question is: which process is actually running on 3104 right now, and why is it returning 500?\n\nLooking at the logs, the v8 version says \"starting on port 3104\" but then returns 500 Internal Server Error. That means the server started successfully but something in the request handling is failing. The workspace version has a bug where it's hardcoded to 8080, so that's probably not the issue.\n\nI should check the uvicorn error logs more carefully - they might show a traceback that explains what's actually crashing when requests come in.","thinkingSignature":"1e7795928476d4b438d514d4c51b42517c55352ea4755b065e1f3d8151672a8d"},{"type":"text","text":"\n\n发现关键问题：workspace 版本 api_server.py 硬编码端口 **8080**，不是 3104！同时 v8 版本虽然在 3104 上，但返回 500。\n\n需要同时修两个问题：\n\n1. v8 版本 500 错误（检查 uvicorn 实际日志）\n2. workspace 版本端口硬编码错误\n"},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_b89936d3f2ac48b28490ea2c","name":"exec","arguments":{"command":"cat /home/ai/.openclaw/v8/scene-classifier/api_server.py | grep -A 5 'if __name__'"}}],"api":"anthropic-messages","provider":"minimax","model":"MiniMax-M2.7","usage":{"input":615,"output":751,"cacheRead":47360,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":48726,"cost":{"input":0.00018449999999999999,"output":0.0009012,"cacheRead":0.0028415999999999997,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0.0039273}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1776054645437,"responseId":"062ba47580df6fd5c7dc4d176be63846"}}
