{"type":"message","id":"6e74aed5","parentId":"6bb27157","timestamp":"2026-04-13T04:38:51.943Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"There's a systemd service for openclaw-router that's in \"activating\" state. The openclaw-router service is trying to start and restart repeatedly. This is why the old v8 version keeps getting restarted.\n\nThe service files exist:\n- openclaw-context.service (running)\n- openclaw-router.service (activating/auto-restart - failing repeatedly)\n- openclaw-ws-proxy.service (activating/auto-restart - failing)\n\nThis means my kill only works temporarily - systemd will restart the service immediately.\n\nI need to:\n1. Stop the systemd services first\n2. Then start my version\n\nOr alternatively, I should fix the openclaw-router service since it's the one causing the v8 scene-classifier to restart.\n\n\nI'll stop the services, clear the port, and start the fixed workspace version instead.","thinkingSignature":"ceab822e3d999966fa18c12f3cad6828b6751dbcbc147294ce90464b2517f7ed"},{"type":"text","text":"\n\n**思考**：发现有 systemd service 在自动重启，导致旧版一直占着端口。需要先停服务。\n\n```\nopenclaw-router.service   → activating/auto-restart（一直失败重试）\nopenclaw-ws-proxy.service → activating/auto-restart（一直失败重试）\n```\n\n这解释了为什么之前 pid 442 的进程一直存在——systemd 在自动拉起。\n\n\n"},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_a4bf1811d15d4fb9bb4fa68a","name":"exec","arguments":{"command":"systemctl stop openclaw-router.service openclaw-ws-proxy.service 2>/dev/null\nsleep 1\nps aux | grep 'api_server\\|openclaw' | grep -v grep\nlsof -i :3104 2>/dev/null || echo \"3104 free\""}}],"api":"anthropic-messages","provider":"minimax","model":"MiniMax-M2.7","usage":{"input":161,"output":319,"cacheRead":55296,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":55776,"cost":{"input":0.000048299999999999995,"output":0.0003828,"cacheRead":0.00331776,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0.0037488599999999997}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1776055122569,"responseId":"062ba6522504b883d17cd3d233818044"}}
