{"type":"message","id":"1917bfae","parentId":"0e52f6d2","timestamp":"2026-04-13T04:39:27.453Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"It worked! The 3104 endpoint now returns a proper JSON response without the 500 error. The confidence is now a float (0.528...) instead of numpy.float32.\n\nBut wait - the response doesn't have a `label` field. It has `scene` instead of `label`. Let me check what the gateway expects. Looking at context.json earlier, it had `classification: null` which suggests the gateway might be looking for a `label` field.\n\nActually wait - let me re-read the response. It returned `scene` not `label`. And the context.json showed `classification: null`. This might mean the gateway hook is using a different field name.\n\nLet me check the current state more carefully.","thinkingSignature":"592649bb6710a53c35793386498a3216c600ab1bfb72cc4aab322fd36b93666e"},{"type":"text","text":"\n\n**3104 工作了！**\n\n```json\n{\n  \"response\": \"[LLM响应] 基于你的输入，建议操作如下：...\",\n  \"intercepted\": false,\n  \"scene\": \"clarify\",\n  \"meta\": \"ambiguous\",\n  \"confidence\": 0.5280722379684448\n}\n```\n\n注意返回字段是 `scene` 不是 `label`，而且 `confidence` 是 Python float（不再是 numpy 类型）。\n\n---\n\n## Step 4：验证链路\n\n**思考**：3104 现在正常了。接下来验证：\n1. 3104 响应字段是否和 gateway 期望的匹配（`label` vs `scene`）\n2. 3103 scorer 是否被调用\n3. openclaw-router 的问题\n\n先发一条消息触发 hook，看 context.json 是否有分类写入。\n"},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_7f69d261cbfa43bba89af843","name":"exec","arguments":{"command":"cat ~/.openclaw/sessions/agent:main:main/context.json 2>/dev/null | python3 -m json.tool 2>/dev/null | head -20"}}],"api":"anthropic-messages","provider":"minimax","model":"MiniMax-M2.7","usage":{"input":165,"output":370,"cacheRead":56128,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":56663,"cost":{"input":0.0000495,"output":0.000444,"cacheRead":0.0033676799999999996,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0.0038611799999999996}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1776055156757,"responseId":"062ba674ed1894fa25f3750d