{"type":"message","id":"457b7653","parentId":"69f1e8be","timestamp":"2026-04-13T04:43:21.222Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"Now I can see the full picture. openclaw-router.js is an Express-based HTTP router that:1. Loads various config files from ~/.openclaw/config/\n2. Uses `@isaced/ai-router` for AI routing\n3. Has routes like /classify and /score that call v8Client\n4. Acts as a proxy/router between gateway and v8 engines\n\nBut the critical files (`clients/v8Client.js` and the `@isaced/ai-router` package) are missing. This means the router was never fully deployed.\n\nLet me check the cron @reboot entry - it was trying to start this router but it always failed due to dotenv first, then these missing dependencies.\n\n\nThe @reboot cron job has been attempting to launch this broken router every time the system starts, which explains why it never successfully initialized.","thinkingSignature":"c59d2ce3c20dd86cc8de6e63b59737b1094b515f991070ecf392c7856b694795"},{"type":"text","text":"\n\n**openclaw-router 是什么**\n\n一个 Express HTTP 路由服务，夹在 gateway 和 v8 引擎之间：\n\n```\ngateway (3102) → openclaw-router (3102 端口) → 路由到 3103/3104/3101\n```\n\n**设计用途**（从代码看）：\n- `/classify` → 调用 v8Client 分类\n- `/score` → 调用 v8Client 评分\n- `/route` → 根据配置路由到不同 provider\n- weather_report.sh 原本往这里发天气消息\n\n**实际问题**：\n\n```javascript\n// 这两个核心依赖不存在\nconst { classify, score } = require('./clients/v8Client');  // 文件不存在\nconst { AIRouter } = require('@isaced/ai-router');           // npm 包不存在\n```\n\n**结论**：\n\nopenclaw-router 是一个**半成品**——代码写了但依赖没装、文件没建。systemd 的 auto-restart 一直试图拉起它，但每次都立即崩掉，所以它从来没能真正路由任何流量。\n\n天气脚本往无效的 router 发，cron 的 @reboot 也一直失败，原因都是同一个：这个服务从未完整部署过。\n\n**如果要让它跑起来**，需要：\n1. 搞清楚 `clients/v8Client.js` 原本应该做什么\n2. 解决 `@isaced/ai-router` 的来源（私有 npm 包？需要 npm install？）\n3. 补全 config 文件\n\n**或者**：如果 router 不是核心链路的一部分（gateway 直接调 3103/3104），可以直接 disable 这几个 systemd service，不让它们再捣乱。\n\n你们当时部署的时候，openclaw-router 是计划用来做什么的？"}],"api":"anthropic-messages","provider":"minimax","model":"MiniMax-M2.7","usage":{"input":396,"output":520,"cacheRead":60096,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":61012,"cost":{"input":0.0001188,"output":0.000624,"cacheRead":0.0036057599999999995,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0.00434856}},"stopReason":"stop","timestamp":1776055388430,"responseId":"062ba75b332ae87983c1e2d8c5384cf2"}}
