{"type":"message","id":"4e2e4de7","parentId":"26d5fa15","timestamp":"2026-04-13T04:49:10.665Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"So when I call directly with `prompt`, it returns 41. So the hook should be working. But context.json shows scoring score: 0. This means either:\n1. The hook is not being triggered\n2. The hook is failing silently\n3. The hook ran but wrote to a different session directory\n\nWait - I just sent a message from the control UI (webchat). Let me check if the hook got triggered and what it wrote. The session key for this conversation should be \"agent:main:main\" or similar.\n\nActually, let me check the current context.json again after my most recent curl test.","thinkingSignature":"3977d0e85b7eae7408bb3a623ac0e907342846c053cb770cee8de337776c9503"},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_018e95d3447643d7932a8c2f","name":"exec","arguments":{"command":"cat ~/.openclaw/sessions/agent:main:main/context.json 2>/dev/null | python3 -m json.tool 2>/dev/null"}}],"api":"anthropic-messages","provider":"minimax","model":"MiniMax-M2.7","usage":{"input":208,"output":179,"cacheRead":67392,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":67779,"cost":{"input":0.0000624,"output":0.0002148,"cacheRead":0.004043519999999999,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0.004320719999999999}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1776055741877,"responseId":"062ba8bd56b05894ed2de292149c5847"}}
