{"type":"message","id":"051b669a","parentId":"7ca61e75","timestamp":"2026-04-13T04:54:11.546Z","message":{"role":"user","content":[{"type":"text","text":"Sender (untrusted metadata):\n```json\n{\n  \"label\": \"openclaw-control-ui\",\n  \"id\": \"openclaw-control-ui\"\n}\n```\n\n[Mon 2026-04-13 12:54 GMT+8] 需要吗"}],"timestamp":1776056051535}}
{"type":"message","id":"08679945","parentId":"051b669a","timestamp":"2026-04-13T04:54:19.026Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"The user is asking if openclaw-router is needed at all. Let me give a direct, clear answer.","thinkingSignature":"3f6d1e64d977d0654749b020dc9eac405270f8e5e3b2459a01ba0b01e26ec9be"},{"type":"text","text":"\n\n**不需要。**\n\n理由：\n\n1. **当前链路已经通**：\n   ```\n   gateway (3102) ← 直接处理请求\n         ↓\n   auto-score-classify hook → 3104 分类 ✅\n                           → 3103 评分 ✅\n                           → context.json ✅\n   ```\n\n2. **router 是额外层，不是必需层**。它的设计目标（多 agent 路由、智能选择 LLM provider）当前系统还没用到。\n\n3. **它一直在后台徒劳重试**——systemd auto-restart 每 3 秒拉一次，每次立即崩掉，产生大量日志。\n\n---\n\n**处理方式**：\n\n```bash\n# 停止并 disable 这两个一直失败的 service\nsystemctl stop openclaw-router.service openclaw-ws-proxy.service\nsystemctl disable openclaw-router.service openclaw-ws-proxy.service\n```\n\n这样系统更干净，也不会有无意义的重试日志。将来如果真的需要多 agent 路由，再重新评估 router 是否值得完整实现。\n\n---\n\n继续配 cron？"}],"api":"anthropic-messages","provider":"minimax","model":"MiniMax-M2.7","usage":{"input":620,"output":232,"cacheRead":72192,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":73044,"cost":{"input":0.000186,"output":0.0002784,"cacheRead":0.004331519999999999,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0.0047959199999999995}},"stopReason":"stop","timestamp":1776056051555,"responseId":"062ba9f3e20fae2ce119607aaa9bbedd"}}
