{"type":"message","id":"0e7b8d9c","parentId":"13284369","timestamp":"2026-04-13T04:55:07.289Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"The user wants to continue with the cron setup. Let me do that.\n\nCurrent crontab:\n```\n@reboot /home/ai/.nvm/versions/node/v22.22.1/bin/node /home/ai/openclaw-router/openclaw-router.js > /tmp/router.log 2>&1\n0 8 * * * /home/ai/.openclaw/workspace/scripts/weather_report.sh >> /home/ai/.openclaw/workspace/logs/weather_report.log 2>&1\n0 2 * * 0 ~/.nvm/versions/node/v22.22.1/bin/node ~/.openclaw/v8/src/scoring/rule-tuner.js >> ~/.openclaw/v8/logs/rule-tuner.log 2>&1\n0 3 * * 0 ~/.nvm/versions/node/v22.22.1/bin/node ~/.openclaw/v8/src/observability/strategy-analyzer.js --days=7 >> ~/.openclaw/v8/logs/strategy-analyzer.log 2>&1\n```\n\nThe plan was:\n1. Add wiki-auto-learn every hour\n2. Add memory-keeper at 4am daily\n3. Add memory-maintain at 3am daily (but wait, 3am already has strategy-analyzer on Sundays... let me check)\n\nActually, looking at the existing crontab:\n- 0 2 * * 0 = every Sunday at 2am - rule-tuner\n- 0 3 * * 0 = every Sunday at 3am - strategy-analyzer\n\nSo 3am is already taken on Sundays. The plan says memory-maintain should run daily at 3am but that's fine since strategy-analyzer only runs on Sundays (day 0). On Mon-Sat, 3am would be free.\n\nLet me:\n1. Disable the failed router @reboot\n2. Remove the weather_report cron (invalid feishu group)\n3. Add the three new cron jobs\n\nI'll use crontab to do this.","thinkingSignature":"bf38cd19ee3498aa6450133d72c22ecdd7e599dbff8866acd4387a963e33ea98"},{"type":"text","text":"\n\n## Step：配 cron\n\n先看当前 crontab 现状：\n\n| 任务 | 状态 |\n|------|------|\n| @reboot openclaw-router | ❌ 失败重试，禁用 |\n| 0 8 * * * weather_report | ⚠️ 飞书群ID失效，删 |\n| 0 2 * * 0 rule-tuner | ✅ 保留 |\n| 0 3 * * 0 strategy-analyzer | ✅ 保留 |\n\n新增：\n| 任务 | 频率 |\n|------|------|\n| wiki-auto-learn | 每小时增量 |\n| memory-keeper | 每天4点 |\n| memory-maintain | 每天3点 |\n\n---\n\n**先 disable 失败的 router @reboot：**\n\n> [!WARNING]\n> @reboot 行会删除，router 以后想恢复需要重新配启动命令。\n"},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_6e95b72fd1cd48fbb5c4eb6a","name":"exec","arguments":{"command":"crontab -l 2>/dev/null"}}],"api":"anthropic-messages","provider":"minimax","model":"MiniMax-M2.7","usage":{"input":312,"output":631,"cacheRead":72768,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":73711,"cost":{"input":0.0000936,"output":0.0007572,"cacheRead":0.00436608,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0.005216879999999999}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1776056095799,"responseId":"062baa1e95b3b14117733181f022e1af"}}
