{"type":"message","id":"83c5ae5d","parentId":"b48fe90c","timestamp":"2026-04-13T04:57:39.750Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"The context.json shows classification with a recent timestamp (04:57:22) matching exactly this message \"现在我发信息你会进行评分和分类吗\". And scoring shows score: 0 which is correct for this simple question.\n\nSo yes, the hook IS firing on every message I receive! The classification shows \"scene\": \"clarify\", \"meta\": \"ambiguous\" which makes sense for this vague question. And scoring shows 0 (simple question, no risk).\n\nLet me verify by checking the current timestamp vs the context.json timestamp.","thinkingSignature":"318de738a44f21edffe6ce74a4a908473dfd283e9d8c6ff87c81d6eb07fb0ea8"},{"type":"text","text":"\n\n**会的，而且已经在做了。**\n\ncontext.json 显示的就是刚才这条消息的结果：\n\n```\n\"messagePreview\": \"[Mon 2026-04-13 12:57 GMT+8] 现在我发信息你会进行评分和分类吗\"\n\"timestamp\": \"2026-04-13T04:57:22.408Z\"\n\"classification\": { \"scene\": \"clarify\", \"confidence\": 0.608 }\n\"scoring\": { \"score\": 0, \"recommendedStrategy\": \"DIRECT\" }\n```\n\n每条消息进来，hook 并行调 3104 和 3103，结果写入 context.json。\n\n现在这条也不例外——分类识别为 `clarify`（需要澄清的模糊请求），评分 0（简单问答）。"}],"api":"anthropic-messages","provider":"minimax","model":"MiniMax-M2.7","usage":{"input":411,"output":268,"cacheRead":75008,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":75687,"cost":{"input":0.0001233,"output":0.0003216,"cacheRead":0.004500479999999999,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0.004945379999999999}},"stopReason":"stop","timestamp":1776056250975,"responseId":"062baabaa2176c68a1d9e78677d2e377"}}
