{"type":"message","id":"ae81569f","parentId":"435d7f68","timestamp":"2026-04-13T05:02:29.762Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"There's a cron called \"Memory Dreaming Promotion\" that was listed in the framework gaps scan from yesterday. Let me check what that was. The scan showed:\n\n```\nCron: Memory Dreaming Promotion  ✅ 每天3点\n```\n\nBut I don't see a script for it. Let me check the cron jobs I have vs what the scan reported.\n\nActually wait, looking at the crontab I just installed - there's no \"Memory Dreaming Promotion\" cron. The scan from yesterday showed 3 crons:\n- Cron: memory-maintain ✅ 每天3点\n- Cron: Memory Dreaming Promotion ✅ 每天3点\n\n\n- Cron: memory-keeper ✅ 每天4点\n\nBut the current crontab only has memory-maintain at 3am and memory-keeper at 4am - Memory Dreaming Promotion is missing. The scan also mentioned LLM Wiki Ingest wasn't automated yet, which aligns with what I'm seeing here.\n\nLooking at the memory-tool.py script, it uses Ollama for vector embeddings to store and search memories, but the cron that would run it hourly isn't actually in the crontab yet. I need to check if there's a wiki-auto-learn cron that should be handling the hourly LLM ingestion.\n","thinkingSignature":"de462cf385e9d7fd176c6d5fa8d8a453267a39204cb911d6d2894a72e76551f6"},{"type":"text","text":"\n\n找到了，记忆系统有多个组件：\n\n**已有的记忆工具**：\n\n| 工具 | 功能 | cron 状态 |\n|------|------|-----------|\n| `memory-tool.py` | 向量记忆（Ollama bge-m3 embeddings） | ❌ 没配 cron |\n| `memory_keeper.sh` | 记忆管理员：扫描/合并/过期检查/session提取 | ✅ 每天4点 |\n| `memory_maintain.sh` | 备份/格式校验/去重 | ✅ 每天3点 |\n\n**但缺少一个关键机制**：session 过程中有价值的信息不会自动进入 memory/。`memory_keeper.sh` 依赖 cron 每天跑一次，但它做的事情是从归档 session 和 ephemeral 目录提取信息，不是实时写入。\n\n---\n\n**你说的\"安装过的技能\"指的是哪个**？是这些脚本还是之前提到但没找到的其他记忆组件？"}],"api":"anthropic-messages","provider":"minimax","model":"MiniMax-M2.7","usage":{"input":79274,"output":434,"cacheRead":1216,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":80924,"cost":{"input":0.0237822,"output":0.0