{"type":"message","id":"9ebf6846","parentId":"1f338db2","timestamp":"2026-04-13T05:07:39.367Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"The user wants to compare the pros and cons of the three options I presented. Let me think through each clearly.\n\nOption 1: context-continuity skill\nOption 2: Use existing components (memory-tool.py, memory_keeper.sh)\nOption 3: Natural session-summary on /new\n\nLet me be honest and direct.","thinkingSignature":"6671cfea462eb406298445cc0c8daf37a11054597241348485afeeedfd258af0"},{"type":"text","text":"\n\n| | **context-continuity** | **现有组件自己搭** | **等 /new 自然摘要** |\n|---|---|---|---|\n| **优点** | 开箱即用，买了就能用 | 安全可控，代码自己审查过 | 零配置，架构原本就是这样 |\n| **缺点** | medium suspicious，需要 --force；自动写所有对话，无 opt-in | 需要自己写一个轻量 cron 脚本 | 只在 /new 时记一次，当次 session 内的信息断层 |\n| **记忆粒度** | 每条消息都记（过度） | 可以设计成每小时/关键节点记 | session 结束才记 |\n| **隐私风险** | 高（所有对话未经确认写入磁盘） | 低（自己控制写什么） | 无额外风险 |\n| **维护成本** | 外部依赖，需跟进更新 | 基本无维护 | 无需维护 |\n\n---\n\n**我的判断**：\n\n- 如果你希望**每条消息都被记住**（不丢失任何上下文）→ 用现有组件搭一个轻量定时写入\n- 如果你只要求**下次 /new 时记得上次做什么**→ 当前架构已经支持\n\ncontext-continuity 的\"自动写所有对话\"在这个场景下是**过度设计**，反而有隐私和存储风险。"}],"api":"anthropic-messages","provider":"minimax","model":"MiniMax-M2.7","usage":{"input":83599,"output":333,"cacheRead":1216,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":85148,"cost":{"input":0.0250797,"output":0.00039959999999999996,"cacheRead":0.00007295999999999999,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0.02555226}},"stopReason":"stop","timestamp":1776056846531,"responseId":"062bad0eb9d7b6fdb8dc15854a69abf5"}}
