{"type":"message","id":"dfe3fce3","parentId":"64f63838","timestamp":"2026-04-13T05:08:56.876Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"The user is asking whether recording every single message would be bad for performance. Let me think about this practically.\n\n**Writing to disk every message**:\n- A single write to an SSD is very fast (microseconds to milliseconds)\n- It's async/non-blocking in most implementations\n- The bottleneck would be if the LLM is being called to process/summarize each message in real-time\n- Just writing raw text to a file is negligible\n\n**What context-continuity actually does** (from the security scan):\n- \"append every conversation to memory/YYYY-MM-DD.md and MEMORY.md\"\n- \"read the last 7 days of memory via shell commands (echo, cat, date)\"\n\n\n- It's just appending text to files, which is essentially free in terms of I/O. The real question isn't whether writing is expensive—it isn't—but whether storing every message creates problems down the line. You still need to read from those files later, and that context window fills up fast if you're pulling in a full day's conversation history every time.\n","thinkingSignature":"0399d20b6305a2aa3bef3664cf283bd184661c7bb446528677a378f828c2d763"},{"type":"text","text":"\n\n不会。写一条消息到 SSD 是微秒级操作，跟 I/O 比不值一提。\n\n**真正的性能问题不在写入，在读取**：\n\n```\n每条消息都写入 → memory/ 膨胀 → 下次读取时文件巨大 → 加载慢 / token 爆炸\n```\n\n当前 session 的消息如果条条都记，一天下来可能是几千条消息。7 天就是几万条。\n\n**更关键的问题不是性能，是检索**：\n\n记了这么多，下次 \"继续\" 时：\n- 全部加载？token 爆掉\n- 随便截取？记了等于没记\n- 向量搜索挑相关条目？需要 embedding 模型排队跑\n\n---\n\n**结论**：性能不会拉胯，但**记了没用、读不出来**才是真正问题。\n\ncontext-continuity 的设计本身就有缺陷——海量写入 + 没法高效检索，不如只在 session 结束前生成一条高质量摘要（当前 session-summary 的做法）。"}],"api":"anthropic-messages","provider":"minimax","model":"MiniMax-M2.7","usage":{"input":83930,"output":403,"cacheRead":1216,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":85549,"cost":{"input":0.025179,"output":0.0004836,"cacheRead":0.00007295999999999999,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0.02573556}},"stopReason":"stop","timestamp":1776056925147,"responseId":"062bad5b1a49844e55bf5fbc64a06004"}}
