{"type":"message","id":"2191955d","parentId":"381fdf73","timestamp":"2026-04-13T05:17:00.890Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"The user wants a rigorous, critical review of the current memory system. Let me think deeply and critically about what's actually wrong with the current system, what's missing, and what the real problems are.\n\nLet me look at what we actually have:\n\n1. **context.json** - stores classification and scoring per message (in current session)\n2. **session-summary hook** - generates summary on /new\n3. **memory_keeper.sh** - runs daily cron, extracts from archived sessions\n4. **memory_maintain.sh** - runs daily cron, backup/maintenance\n5. **wiki-auto-learn** - runs hourly, ingests to wiki\n6. **MEMORY.md** - long-term memory file (currently empty)\n\n\n7. **memory/** - daily notes\n\nNow I'm seeing the critical problems with this architecture. The memory system has no active participation during conversations—it's purely passive. The session-summary hook only fires on /new, which means there's no mechanism for capturing insights or decisions that happen mid-session. Meanwhile, context.json is being written to constantly but never actually read back to inform ongoing behavior. And the whole system is anchored to /new as the trigger, which means valuable context that emerges during a session gets lost when that session eventually ends.\n\nThe cron jobs are running, but they're operating on stale data—the memory_keeper is processing archived sessions, not generating new memories from what's actually happening. The bootstrap mechanism exists theoretically but hasn't been validated in practice, so I don't know if it's actually helping or just adding noise. And the metadata from classification and scoring is being collected but not used for anything actionable.\n\nLooking at the root causes: there's no active capture mechanism during conversations, context.json is written to constantly but never read back, and memory/ is just storing data without any retrieval logic. The real issue is that the system is collecting everything but not doing anything meaningful with it. The fix would be simpler than a full metadata-driven system—I just need event-driven capture on important signals, something to consolidate context.json into memory/ephemeral, and a way to read from memory/ when generating responses.","thinkingSignature":"043bdee869a4de7739c30aef708b57dda6396e98dacea2dee6087d7a19dbb5b8"},{"type":"text","text":"\n\n## 严格评审：当前记忆系统\n\n---\n\n### 系统现状\n\n| 组件 | 实际状态 |\n|------|---------|\n| `memory/` 文件 | ✅ 有历史积累（从3月31日至今） |\n| `MEMORY.md` | ❌ 空的 |\n| `context.json` | ✅ 每条消息写入，但从未被读取 |\n| `session-summary` | ⚠️ 只在 /new 触发，从未验证 |\n| `bootstrap` | ⚠️ 从未验证（凌晨被 SIGKILL 中断） |\n| `memory_keeper.sh` | ✅ 跑了4个月，但从 session 提取知识的能力未验证 |\n| cron 配置 | ⚠️ 今天才配，之前记忆层实际是死的 |\n\n---\n\n### 根本问题\n\n**问题1：context.json 是单向写入，从未被使用**\n\n每条消息写入 classification/scoring，但没有任何组件读取它。context.json 是死数据。\n\n**问题2：session-summary 是唯一的聚合点，但它只在 /new 触发**\n\n如果用户连续 3 天在一个 session 里聊，session-summary 永远不会跑，这3天的关键信息永远不会进 memory/。\n\n**问题3：memory_keeper.sh 从 session 提取的是原始 message text，不是 structured insight**\n\n从 session 提取的格式是 `\"text\":\"xxx\"`，是一整段原始对话，不是\"决策：xxx，结论：xxx\"。这样的提取价值极低。\n\n**问题4：没有任何组件在对话过程中主动写入 memory**\n\n整个记忆层是被动的，没有实时捕获能力。\n\n---\n\n### 关键矛盾\n\n| 矛盾 | 说明 |\n|------|------|\n| 写入丰富，读出贫乏 | context.json 每条消息都在写，但没有读 |\n| 存储充足，触发稀少 | memory/ 文件多，但 session-summary 只在 /new 触发 |\n| 聚合存在，实时缺失 | session-summary 是好的设计，但它不是实时的 |\n\n---\n\n### 真实评级\n\n| 维度 | 评分 | 说明 |\n|------|------|------|\n| 基础设施 | 6/10 | cron 刚配，之前一直缺失 |\n| 实时捕获 | 1/10 | 完全没有 |\n| 读取利用 | 1/10 | context.json 写了但没人读 |\n| 聚合质量 | 4/10 | session-summary 设计合理，但未验证 |\n| 跨 session 连续性 | 3/10 | bootstrap 未验证，MEMORY.md 空 |\n\n**总分：3/10**——记忆系统大部分时间是死的。\n\n---\n\n### 最需要修的\n\n1. **context.json 从未被读取** — 这是最浪费的部分，每条消息的分类评分都白写了\n2. **没有实时捕获** — 只能等 /new，但 session 可能持续很久\n3. **memory_keeper.sh 提取质量低** — 提原始 text 不提 structured insight\n\n---\n\n### 结论\n\n**不是缺某个技能的问题，是整个记忆层没有形成闭环：**\n\n```\n写入 → 聚合 → 读取 → 利用\n  ↓       ↓       ↓     ↓\n context  session  memory bootstrap\n  .json  -summary   /     /\n                ephemeral\n```\n\n现在只有左侧勉强通，右侧全是断的。修 context.json 被读取 + 实时捕获，比装任何新技能都重要。"}],"api":"anthropic-messages","provider":"minimax","model":"MiniMax-M2.7","usage":{"input":85811,"output":1102,"cacheRead":1152,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":88065,"cost":{"input":0.0257433,"output":0.0013223999999999998,"cacheRead":0.00006911999999999999,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0.02713482}},"stopReason":"stop","timestamp":1776057391580,"responseId":"062baf2f1d1ef0c92ab0a1bd3f6945b8"}}
