{"type":"message","id":"9efe414d","parentId":"98412eec","timestamp":"2026-04-13T05:20:21.161Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"The user is reminding me about the idea we discussed earlier - using metadata (classification/scoring) to trigger real-time memory writes to memory/ephemeral/. They want to know what happened to that proposal. We were discussing a design where:\n\n1. When a message comes in → 3104 classify + 3103 score\n2. If score >= threshold OR intercepted == true OR other metadata signals\n3. Write a structured note to memory/ephemeral/\n4. memory_keeper.sh merges daily\n\nI was about to propose implementing this when the user said \"再思考一下\" (think more), then \"犀利严格的评审\" (ruthlessly evaluate), and then \"现在怎么说\" (what do you say now).\n\n\nThe user is pushing me to actually move forward with this instead of continuing to analyze. They've been patient with my back-and-forth, so I should just start building it.","thinkingSignature":"0acabed98711a51f2c26c5d518c7370bd1867021336fba1ea6c35f1a170dfb9a"},{"type":"text","text":"\n\n还在。现在就做。\n\n**方案**：hook 每条消息写入 context.json → 扩展成同时写 memory/ephemeral/，用 metadata 过滤。\n\n**实现位置**：`~/.openclaw/hooks/auto-score-classify/handler.js`\n\n**触发条件**（满足任一即写入）：\n\n```javascript\nconst shouldRemember = (\n  scoring.score >= 50 ||                              // 复杂任务\n  scoring.recommendedStrategy === 'SPAWN_SUBAGENT' || // 需要子代理\n  scoring.recommendedStrategy === 'MEGA_TASK' ||     // 巨型任务\n  classification.intercepted === true ||              // 高风险拦截\n  classification.scene === 'fault_recovery' ||       // 故障处理\n  text.includes('记住') ||\n  text.includes('以后都') ||\n  text.includes('决定用')\n);\n```\n\n写入格式：\n```markdown\n## [timestamp] 关键信息\n\n**场景**: {scene}\n**评分**: score={score}, strategy={recommendedStrategy}\n**消息**: {messagePreview}\n**决策/结论**: {LLM分析一句话}\n```\n\n---\n\n**现在动手改 handler.js？**"}],"api":"anthropic-messages","provider":"minimax","model":"MiniMax-M2.7","usage":{"input":86844,"output":423,"cacheRead":1152,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":88419,"cost":{"input":0.0260532,"output":0.0005076,"cacheRead":0.00006911999999999999,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0.026629919999999998}},"stopReason":"stop","timestamp":1776057607836,"responseId":"062bb0067a5d20355c23b4c3db2f137b"}}
