{"type":"message","id":"ab5d0b40","parentId":"d2b11a39","timestamp":"2026-04-13T05:26:39.212Z","message":{"role":"user","content":[{"type":"text","text":"Sender (untrusted metadata):\n```json\n{\n  \"label\": \"openclaw-control-ui\",\n  \"id\": \"openclaw-control-ui\"\n}\n```\n\n[Mon 2026-04-13 13:26 GMT+8] 那能不能实时写入保障记忆安全，等到new再把这些记忆更新"}],"timestamp":1776057999199}}
{"type":"message","id":"42d77929","parentId":"ab5d0b40","timestamp":"2026-04-13T05:26:58.955Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"The user is asking: can we do both? Real-time writes to memory for safety, then when /new happens, those real-time entries get updated/refined into session summaries.\n\nThis is actually a good synthesis:\n- Real-time: write key moments to memory/ephemeral/ (safety net - don't lose anything)\n- /new: session-summary reads ephemeral + context.json, generates refined summary, clears ephemeral\n\nThis is not contradictory - it's a two-tier system:\n1. Safety net: real-time captures (may be noisy,碎片)\n2. Refinement: session-summary聚合 + 提炼\n\nLet me think about whether this actually works:\n\n\nThe ephemeral layer would capture key decisions without needing LLM analysis - just structured metadata like \"decision: openclaw-router is disable because missing core dependency\" with timestamps and classification data. Then session-summary reads both the real-time captures and context.json when /new fires, using the LLM to synthesize everything into a clean summary while clearing out the ephemeral layer. This avoids the mess of trying to do LLM analysis in the hook while still preserving important moments as they happen.\n\nThe approach is actually sound: don't require LLM in the hook, batch the refinement to /new, and keep ephemeral as a temporary staging area rather than a permanent store. The user seems to be pointing out that these two strategies complement each other - real-time capture ensures nothing is lost, and the periodic refinement prevents the hook from becoming a bloated storage layer.","thinkingSignature":"f6ebf98913887f4238fd63384f98d883a0dc2475faf9fbc296ec095b88c5f56f"},{"type":"text","text":"\n\n对，这正是最合理的两层设计：\n\n---\n\n## 两层记忆方案\n\n**第一层：实时安全网（hook 做）**\n- 每条消息的 metadata（score、scene、intercepted）实时写 `memory/ephemeral/`\n- 碎片化、低质量，但**不丢东西**\n- 不调用 LLM，纯 metadata 写入\n\n**第二层：/new 时提炼（session-summary 做）**\n- 读取 ephemeral/ + context.json\n- LLM 提炼成结构化摘要\n- 写 `memory/YYYY-MM-DD-summary.md`\n- 清空 ephemeral/\n\n---\n\n**为什么这个方案可行**：\n\n| 问题 | 解法 |\n|------|------|\n| 不想每条消息都记 | metadata 触发，只记有意义的（score>=50/intercepted/fault_recovery） |\n| hook 不能调用 LLM | 不调用，只写 metadata |\n| 碎片化没价值 | /new 时 LLM 提炼 |\n| context.json 白写了 | 复用，session-summary 读它也读 ephemeral |\n\n---\n\n**实现起来很简单**：\n\nhook 里加 10 行代码：\n\n```javascript\n// metadata 触发写入 ephemeral/\nif (scoring.score >= 50 || classification.intercepted || \n    classification.scene === 'fault_recovery') {\n  writeEphemeral({ text, classification, scoring, timestamp });\n}\n```\n\nsession-summary 已经是 LLM 驱动的，只需要加一行：读取 ephemeral/ 并入摘要。\n\n---\n\n**要做吗？**"}],"api":"anthropic-messages","provider":"minimax","model":"MiniMax-M2.7","usage":{"input":88786,"output":609,"cacheRead":1216,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":90611,"cost":{"input":0.026635799999999998,"output":0.0007308,"cacheRead":0.00007295999999999999,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0.027439559999999998}},"stopReason":"stop","timestamp":1776057999223,"responseId":"062bb18e1d51cbe04370b184783a83e5"}}
