{"type":"message","id":"3caea619","parentId":"41a690b5","timestamp":"2026-04-13T05:29:53.910Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"The user is asking about adding metadata on top of the threshold-based filtering. They're probably asking: \"what if we also consider the metadata signals on top of the score threshold to make the filtering more precise?\"\n\nSo the logic would be:\n- Base threshold (score >= 60)\n- PLUS metadata signals that indicate importance\n\nLet me think about what metadata signals would indicate a message is worth remembering, beyond just the score.\n\nThe metadata we have for each message:\n- classification.scene\n- classification.confidence  \n- classification.intercepted\n- classification.meta (confident/low_confidence/ambiguous)\n- scoring.score\n- scoring.recommendedStrategy\n- scoring.factors (logic/risk/duration/resource/uncertainty/dependency)\n\nSignals that indicate \"important\":\n- high risk factor (risk >= 2 or 3) → the task is dangerous, important to remember\n- high uncertainty → involves external APIs, unpredictable, might need to revisit\n- high dependency → complex dependencies, might matter for future context\n- ambiguous classification (meta === 'ambiguous') → user needed clarification, might indicate confusion pattern\n\n\n- low confidence (meta === 'low_confidence') → classifier uncertain, might indicate edge case\n- intercepted === true → already flagged as high risk\n\nSo combining score threshold with these risk factors would give me a more nuanced way to identify which messages truly matter.","thinkingSignature":"ad3a61d3df58c4d5b8a3ecfd74715957f2057c99e0565a027a05cd5fce3167c4"},{"type":"text","text":"\n\n对，**分数阈值 + metadata 信号叠加**，比单纯阈值更精确。\n\n---\n\n**多维度叠加判断：**\n\n```javascript\nconst isMeaningful = (\n  scoring.score >= 60 ||\n  scoring.factors.risk >= 2 ||          // 涉及危险操作，踩过坑要记\n  scoring.factors.uncertainty >= 2 ||   // 依赖外部API，结果不确定，可能重蹈覆辙\n  scoring.factors.dependency >= 2 ||     // 依赖复杂，多模块协作，状态要记\n  scoring.recommendedStrategy === 'SPAWN_SUBAGENT' ||\n  scoring.recommendedStrategy === 'MEGA_TASK' ||\n  classification.intercepted === true ||  // 被拦截的高风险操作，重要\n  classification.scene === 'fault_recovery' ||\n  classification.meta === 'ambiguous'     // 分类歧义，user 可能没表达清楚\n);\n```\n\n---\n\n**为什么这样更合理：**\n\n| 信号 | 含义 |\n|------|------|\n| `risk >= 2` | 危险操作，踩过坑不能再踩 |\n| `uncertainty >= 2` | 外部依赖，结果不稳定，下次可能需要重新处理 |\n| `dependency >= 2` | 涉及多个模块/服务，协调状态要记 |\n| `meta === 'ambiguous'` | 用户意图不清，下次要确认 |\n| `intercepted === true` | 被系统拦截的高风险行为，用户实际想做什么 |\n\n这比单独 `score >= 60` 更准确——**分低也可能重要**（比如一个低分但踩了坑的命令）。\n\n---\n\n**最终触发条件：任一满足即写入**\n\n---\n\n**要做吗？**"}],"api":"anthropic-messages","provider":"minimax","model":"MiniMax-M2.7","usage":{"input":432,"output":627,"cacheRead":90368,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":91427,"cost":{"input":0.0001296,"output":0.0007524,"cacheRead":0.005422079999999999,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0.006304079999999999}},"stopReason":"stop","timestamp":1776058168664,"responseId":"062bb2370909b8be98bc641fe681ec07"}}
