{"type":"message","id":"211b791b","parentId":"4f427017","timestamp":"2026-04-13T05:44:28.801Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"Good. Now let me do a final summary of what we've implemented.","thinkingSignature":"c5d71323558093bb756f77bc86f4c550b422a52a1e863c211c86cfd7a8b592ce"},{"type":"text","text":"语法检查通过。\n\n---\n\n## 完成总结\n\n### 第一层：hook 实时捕获（已实现）\n\n**文件**：`~/.openclaw/hooks/auto-score-classify/handler.js`\n\n**触发条件**：\n```javascript\nisMeaningful = (\n  text.match(/(记住|以后都|决定用|别用|改用|这个要记|记下来)/) ||\n  classification.intercepted === true ||\n  classification.scene === 'fault_recovery' ||\n  scoring.factors.risk >= 3 ||\n  scoring.recommendedStrategy === 'MEGA_TASK'\n);\n```\n\n**写入位置**：`memory/ephemeral/YYYY-MM-DD-HH.jsonl`（按小时分，每条 JSONL）\n\n---\n\n### 第二层：session-summary 提炼 + entity 升格（已实现）\n\n**文件**：`~/.openclaw/hooks/session-summary/handler.js`\n\n**处理流程**：\n1. 读取前一个 session 的 ephemeral 文件（按 `sessionId` 过滤）\n2. 去重 + 限制最多 20 条\n3. LLM 生成摘要 + 判断 entity 升格\n4. 写入 `memory/YYYY-MM-DD-summary.md`\n5. 执行 entity 创建/更新（`memory/entities/*.md`）\n6. 清空 ephemeral（由 memory_keeper.sh 后续处理）\n\n---\n\n### 待验证\n\n下次发 `/new` 时：\n- `memory/ephemeral/` 是否有碎片\n- `memory/YYYY-MM-DD-summary.md` 是否生成\n- `memory/entities/*.md` 是否有升格的 entity\n\n要现在测试一下吗？"}],"api":"anthropic-messages","provider":"minimax","model":"MiniMax-M2.7","usage":{"input":92415,"output":351,"cacheRead":18037,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":110803,"cost":{"input":0.0277245,"output":0.0004212,"cacheRead":0.0010822199999999998,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0.029227919999999998}},"stopReason":"stop","timestamp":1776059056157,"responseId":"062bb5afd547e982d42bb385fa6ff622"}}
