{"type":"message","id":"2a86ac41","parentId":"a93fbb29","timestamp":"2026-04-13T05:51:26.576Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"The test message \"这是测试消息\" was NOT written to ephemeral. The hook is not capturing it. This means either:\n1. The hook is not being triggered (the message came through webchat but maybe didn't trigger the hook)\n2. The hook is running but the isMeaningful check failed (which is correct - \"这是测试消息\" shouldn't be meaningful)\n\nActually, the message \"这是测试消息\" is just a test message and doesn't meet any of the isMeaningful conditions - it has no keywords, no fault_recovery, no intercepted, no risk>=3, etc. \n\nSo it's correct that it wasn't written. \n\nI need to verify the hook is actually running, but the real issue is that I can't send a meaningful message in this context to test it.","thinkingSignature":"46fd43bc95bf23a059705724efaf43424efec44852a6671df96048439bb5e334"},{"type":"text","text":"\"这是测试消息\" 没有触发写入——**这是对的**，因为它不满足任何触发条件：\n- 没有 keyword（记住/决定用等）\n- `intercepted` ≠ true\n- `scene` ≠ `fault_recovery`\n- `risk` < 3\n- `strategy` ≠ `MEGA_TASK`\n\n这条消息是纯测试，hook 正确地过滤掉了。\n\n---\n\n**问题是**：我没有办法在这个 webchat 里发一条\"记住xxx\"来真正测试写入（这会污染记忆）。\n\n**验证方式**：下次发 `/new` 时，整个 session-summary 链路会跑，包括读 ephemeral。那时候才能确认 hook 在正常工作。\n\n或者你可以让这次 session 自然结束（关掉网页），session-summary 会触发。"}],"api":"anthropic-messages","provider":"minimax","model":"MiniMax-M2.7","usage":{"input":96120,"output":312,"cacheRead":18037,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":114469,"cost":{"input":0.028835999999999997,"output":0.0003744,"cacheRead":0.0010822199999999998,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0.030292619999999996}},"stopReason":"stop","timestamp":1776059472037,"responseId":"062bb7505b85b22edf53ecd00a774f85"}}
