{"type":"message","id":"584d3e35","parentId":"3a983795","timestamp":"2026-04-13T06:01:24.611Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"The file reading logic works. \n\nNow, the hook has been updated. But the user can't verify it until a new session starts (bootstrap is triggered). In the current session, I can't test if the injection works.\n\nThe user might be frustrated that I keep talking about testing but can't actually verify in real time. Let me just confirm what was done and tell them to test in the next session.\n\nActually, let me think about whether there's a way to trigger bootstrap in the current session. Looking at the hook event system - it fires on `agent:bootstrap` events. Could I manually trigger a bootstrap event somehow? Probably not from within the session.\n\n\nI should wrap this up and let the user know the hook is ready for the next session to verify.","thinkingSignature":"a891d05a1d7c7532d7cea3912807a5f25cfc32c20d26b530c9aec49e6f3bfee5"},{"type":"text","text":"语法和文件读取都验证通过了。\n\n**现在能做的**：hook 已修改，文件都存在。**无法在当前 session 验证**，因为 bootstrap 只在新 session 启动时触发。\n\n---\n\n**总结这次修改**：\n\n- `hooks/handler.js`（self-improving hook）→ 改为在 bootstrap 时注入 MEMORY.md + 最近3个 session summary\n- `hooks/auto-score-classify/handler.js` → 已有意义消息实时写入 ephemeral/\n- `hooks/session-summary/handler.js` → LLM 提炼 + entity 升格\n\n**下次 /new 时**，bootstrap 会自动把 MEMORY.md 和 2026-04-13-session-summary.md 注入到新 session 的上下文。如果新 session 里的我主动提到了\"框架修复\"或\"2026-04-13\"，说明链路通了。"}],"api":"anthropic-messages","provider":"minimax","model":"MiniMax-M2.7","usage":{"input":102586,"output":330,"cacheRead":18037,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":120953,"cost":{"input":0.0307758,"output":0.000396,"cacheRead":0.0010822199999999998,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0.03225402}},"stopReason":"stop","timestamp":1776060069874,"responseId":"062bb9a5765615e587fcacb5fcac163a"}}
