{"type":"message","id":"150378cc","parentId":"fec51b7e","timestamp":"2026-04-13T06:02:18.741Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"The user is asking if there's real-time memory now. Let me think about this carefully.\n\nThe question is: after all the work done today, is there real-time memory capability?\n\nWhat was implemented:\n1. auto-score-classify hook → writes meaningful messages to ephemeral/ (real-time capture)\n2. session-summary → reads ephemeral + generates summary + promotes to entities (on /new)\n3. bootstrap hook → injects MEMORY.md + recent summaries on new session\n\nBut there's a problem: the auto-score-classify hook writes to ephemeral/, but does the current session (this webchat) actually use the updated hook code? The hook is loaded when the gateway starts. If the gateway was started before we updated the hook, the old code is still running.\n \nThe gateway started at 11:52 and we updated the hook at 13:46, so the running process is still using the old code. The ephemeral files we saw were from our manual writes, not from the hook itself. The real-time memory is technically deployed but not actually active in this session since the hook code hasn't been reloaded.\n\nFor real-time memory to work, we'd need to restart the gateway with `openclaw gateway restart` or trigger a hook reload somehow. So the honest answer is: the code is deployed but inactive because the gateway needs to be restarted to pick up the changes. This is a practical limitation we should address.","thinkingSignature":"6ae8619146e5888c23ff9858dc55387276b4dd93a297311aab5f0c897877a921"},{"type":"text","text":"**部署了，但没在跑。**\n\nauto-score-classify hook 的代码改了，但 gateway 启动时加载的还是旧代码。要让它生效需要重启 gateway。\n\n```bash\nopenclaw gateway restart\n```\n\n重启后，hook 才会用新代码运行。"}],"api":"anthropic-messages","provider":"minimax","model":"MiniMax-M2.7","usage":{"input":54,"output":344,"cacheRead":119485,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":119883,"cost":{"input":0.0000162,"output":0.0004128,"cacheRead":0.007169099999999999,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0.007598099999999999}},"stopReason":"stop","timestamp":1776060112768,"responseId":"062bb9d2889bc4d08435f3772ddbab0b"}}
