{"type":"message","id":"c2817a1e","parentId":"1ca1004d","timestamp":"2026-04-13T06:02:58.161Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"The user wants to see which hook/plan I'm talking about. They're asking me to show them the real-time memory plan (the two-layer system we designed) to review it.\n\nLet me show them the key parts that were implemented.","thinkingSignature":"14886a11db1b5ee38c82679d0279f3e239f08ae885f016ca17978b2e04ad1e34"},{"type":"text","text":"**两层记忆系统**：\n\n---\n\n**第一层：hook 实时捕获（auto-score-classify/handler.js）**\n\n```javascript\n// 触发条件\nconst isMeaningful = (\n  text.match(/(记住|以后都|决定用|别用|改用|这个要记|记下来)/) ||\n  classification.intercepted === true ||\n  classification.scene === 'fault_recovery' ||\n  scoring.factors.risk >= 3 ||\n  scoring.recommendedStrategy === 'MEGA_TASK'\n);\n\n// 满足条件 → 写入 memory/ephemeral/YYYY-MM-DD-HH.jsonl\n```\n\n写入格式：\n```json\n{\n  \"timestamp\": \"2026-04-13T14:02:00+08:00\",\n  \"sessionKey\": \"agent:main:main\",\n  \"text\": \"用户说的原始消息\",\n  \"textPreview\": \"前200字\",\n  \"classification\": { \"scene\": \"...\", \"confidence\": 0.8 },\n  \"scoring\": { \"score\": 75, \"factors\": {...}, \"recommendedStrategy\": \"...\" }\n}\n```\n\n---\n\n**第二层：session-summary 提炼升格（session-summary/handler.js）**\n\n```\nephemeral/ → LLM 提炼 → entity 升格 + 摘要\n```\n\n触发时机：/new 或 session 结束\n\n---\n\n**第三层：bootstrap 注入（handler.js）**\n\n```\n/new 时 → MEMORY.md + 最近3个摘要 → 注入新 session\n```\n\n---\n\n**现在的问题是**：gateway 没重启，hook 用的还是旧代码。第二层和第三层也是新代码，没重启也不生效。"}],"api":"anthropic-messages","provider":"minimax","model":"MiniMax-M2.7","usage":{"input":0,"output":392,"cacheRead":119656,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":120048,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0.0004704,"cacheRead":0.007179359999999999,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0.007649759999999999}},"stopReason":"stop","timestamp":1776060165206,"responseId":"062bba041b378e4debd2c2663d08bcd5"}}
