{"type":"message","id":"d0e8bab0","parentId":"325f0514","timestamp":"2026-04-13T06:12:18.537Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"User is right - I should write the key information from this session into memory right now, while the session is still active. This is the most reliable approach - don't rely on future mechanisms, write it now.","thinkingSignature":"2a2b733e6765f78aebe1511289836c9dc113bf2cea0e84389d243e1c2b0f3796"},{"type":"text","text":"对，现在就写，不等 /new：\n"},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_function_46fgzvpw9w68_1","name":"write","arguments":{"content":"# Session: 2026-04-13 14:00\n\n<!-- summary-only -->\n\n## 主题\n框架修复完成 + 两层记忆系统部署验证\n\n## 关键决策\n1. 3104 classifier 修好（numpy序列化 + workspace Apr 13新版），端口统一3104\n2. 3103 scorer 修好（text字段兼容）\n3. openclaw-router 判定半成品，disable systemd service\n4. cron 重新配置：wiki-auto-learn每小时，memory-keeper每天4点，memory-maintain每天3点\n5. 两层记忆系统部署：hook实时捕获 → ephemeral/ + session-summary LLM提炼\n6. self-improving hook 改写：bootstrap时注入MEMORY.md + 最近3个摘要\n7. gateway 重启完成，hook 实时记忆验证通过\n\n## 重要发现\n1. bootstrap 机制从未验证：AGENTS.md里的指令只是写在文件里，系统没有自动执行\n2. 修复方法：改 self-improving hook，往 bootstrapFiles push MEMORY.md + summaries\n3. ephemeral 触发条件：keyword(记住/决定用等) OR intercepted OR fault_recovery OR risk>=3 OR MEGA_TASK\n4. 实时记忆验证通过（\"记住我用的是 webchat\" → ephemeral写入成功）\n\n## 待跟进\n- [ ] session-summary 在 /new 时跑通（ephemeral → entity升格）\n- [ ] bootstrap 注入在下个 session 验证\n\n<!-- source: agent:main:main -->\n","path":"/home/ai/.openclaw/workspace/memory/2026-04-13-14-session.md"}}],"api":"anthropic-messages","provider":"minimax","model":"MiniMax-M2.7","usage":{"input":54,"output":422,"cacheRead":124477,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":124953,"cost":{"input":0.0000162,"output":0.0005064,"cacheRead":0.00746862,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0.00799122}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1776060713431,"responseId":"062bbc2c3706b0f2c1ff6abe3cb673ac"}}
