{"type":"message","id":"b695ee8f","parentId":"9f03f0ee","timestamp":"2026-04-13T06:13:44.051Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"Now I see the problem! There are TWO instances of `python3 api_server.py` running:1. `24968/24970` - started at 12:55 (from cron wiki-auto-learn)2. `54932/54933` - started at 13:59 (from cron wiki-auto-learn again)3. `57472` - started at 14:04\n\nWait, the PID 57472 is the one listening on 3104. But 57472 is running `/usr/bin/python3 api_server.py` - this is the v8 scene-classifier version, not the workspace version that I fixed!\n\nLet me check what version is running on 3104:","thinkingSignature":"f07eb8051fca5abcb7632457722e6f1e7df6ee85b30500fa81a49ce0ad767cfc"},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_function_x6n8fsw3bzc1_1","name":"exec","arguments":{"command":"readlink /proc/57472/cwd 2>/dev/null; cat /proc/57472/cmdline | tr '\\0' ' '"}}],"api":"anthropic-messages","provider":"minimax","model":"MiniMax-M2.7","usage":{"input":109281,"output":198,"cacheRead":18037,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":127516,"cost":{"input":0.032784299999999995,"output":0.0002376,"cacheRead":0.0010822199999999998,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0.034104119999999995}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1776060816136,"responseId":"062bbc8fe6e29b8e0cfe9814d28a0ac2"}}
