{"type":"message","id":"20995c2c","parentId":"297f7c86","timestamp":"2026-04-13T06:14:28.846Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"3104 is back up and working. Now let me verify the current context.json to see the full picture.","thinkingSignature":"d1f669b428d48421d1a4a89702795bac93c8ff6050833f2253913c7f8546e670"},{"type":"text","text":"3104 恢复正常。\n\n**当前上下文状态**：\n\n```\nclassification: null  ← 刚重启，还没收到消息（timestamp: 06:13）\nscoring: score=0    ← 简单消息，低分\ntimestamp: 06:13    ← 约3分钟前的上下文\nmessagePreview: \"查看上下文\"\n```\n\n**没有 bootstrapFiles 注入**：因为 bootstrap 只在 `/new` 时触发。当前 session 没有重启过，bootstrapFiles 只在 session 第一次启动时注入一次。\n\ncontext.json 是每条消息更新的，不是 session 级别的。bootstrapFiles 应该在 session 启动时就已经注入了，只是不在 context.json 里显示。\n\n**真正的问题是**：3104 又挂了导致 classification=null，但 scoring 还在工作。说明 auto-score-classify hook 在并发调用 3104/3103，其中 3104 返回 null 时不影响 scoring 写入。"}],"api":"anthropic-messages","provider":"minimax","model":"MiniMax-M2.7","usage":{"input":110324,"output":202,"cacheRead":18037,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":128563,"cost":{"input":0.0330972,"output":0.00024239999999999998,"cacheRead":0.0010822199999999998,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0.03442182}},"stopReason":"stop","timestamp":1776060856663,"responseId":"062bbcb86180b6b564f8090bdc40aec1"}}
