{"type":"message","id":"a0633899","parentId":"3e37f4da","timestamp":"2026-04-13T06:15:15.383Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"The user is asking \"怎么样\" - how is it going? Let me give a concise status update.\n\nCurrent state:\n- 3104 is working again (just fixed, workspace version on 3104)\n- context.json shows classification: null (because 3104 just came back up after the restart, and the last message was before the fix)\n- scoring: score=0 (the \"查看上下文\" message is a simple query)\n- The ephemeral is working - we verified it captured \"记住我用的是 webchat\"\n\nKey issues:\n1. 3104 keeps getting replaced by the v8 old version because systemd auto-restart\n2. There's a race condition between the two python processes on 3104\n\n\n3. Need to figure out how to prevent the v8 version from auto-restarting and stealing the port\n\nThe core problem is that systemd keeps reverting to the v8 version, so I either need to disable that auto-restart mechanism or ensure the workspace version gets loaded first.","thinkingSignature":"cc3b0acabf5ab6d05e41316669e338365d5f7b808b26dcb0754c1b80da1b4bdb"},{"type":"text","text":"**现状**：\n\n- 3104 ✅ 刚修好（workspace 版本，numpy修复版）\n- scoring ✅ 工作正常\n- ephemeral ✅ 验证通过\n- 3104 又被 systemd 拉回 v8 旧版 → 需要手动 kill 重启 → **这是个循环 bug**\n\n**根本问题**：\n\nsystemd `openclaw-ws-proxy.service` 每次 gateway 重启都会自动拉起，然后抢占 3104 端口。先前虽然 stop 了，但 gateway 重启本身可能触发了某种联动。\n\n**需要彻底解决**：\n\n禁止 systemd 自动拉起 v8 scene-classifier：\n"},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_function_imzuiy0h7ll0_1","name":"exec","arguments":{"command":"systemctl list-units --type=service | grep -i 'scene\\|classifier\\|openclaw' 2>/dev/null"}}],"api":"anthropic-messages","provider":"minimax","model":"MiniMax-M2.7","usage":{"input":54,"output":379,"cacheRead":126054,"cacheWrite":1776,"totalTokens":128263,"cost":{"input":0.0000162,"output":0.0004548,"cacheRead":0.00756324,"cacheWrite":0.000666,"total":0.00870024}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1776060898759,"resp