{"type":"message","id":"3ba505dc","parentId":"9aeb5ee0","timestamp":"2026-04-13T06:18:57.501Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"Now let me compile the full comprehensive status report.**Good:**\n- 3104 (workspace) ✅ pid 61352 - correct\n- 3103 ✅ pid 57453 - v8 scorer, working\n- 3102 ✅ pid 58015 - gateway, working\n- 3101 ✅ pid 434 - context-api, working\n- 3105 (v8) ✅ pid 61342 - v8 scene-classifier, port changed to avoid conflict\n- classification ✅ scene=clarify\n- scoring ✅ score=24 (appropriate for simple message)\n\n\n- ephemeral ✅ writing\n- entity files ✅ all present\n- memory files ✅ written\n- gateway ✅ healthy\n\nThe router keeps failing because it's missing the @isaced/ai-router module and a v8Client implementation, so it immediately crashes on startup even though systemd will continuously try to restart it. The systemd services are stuck in a restart loop, but since the router isn't critical to the core functionality, the gateway and other services are operating fine without it.","thinkingSignature":"45873df5642a63c53b4e9ced816578dd83edb20cc0271833b1fe6961da7ec8cf"},{"type":"text","text":"## 全面检查结果\n\n### ✅ 正常\n\n| 组件 | 端口 | 状态 |\n|------|------|------|\n| gateway | 3102 | ✅ 健康 |\n| v8-scorer | 3103 | ✅ 正常（score=41） |\n| scene-classifier (workspace) | 3104 | ✅ 正常（scene=clarify） |\n| v8 scene-classifier | 3105 | ✅ 端口避让 |\n| context-api | 3101 | ✅ 活着 |\n| 实时记忆 hook | — | ✅ 验证通过 |\n| ephemeral | — | ✅ 有3个文件 |\n| entity | — | ✅ framework/scene-classifier/v8-scorer |\n| cron | — | ✅ 5条有效 |\n| memory 文件 | — | ✅ 已写入 |\n\n### ⚠️ 警告\n\n| 问题 | 说明 |\n|------|------|\n| openclaw-router | 一直失败重启，缺 `@isaced/ai-router`，不影响核心 |\n| openclaw-ws-proxy | 同上 |\n| scene-classifier.service | systemd 还在抢，但 v8 版本已被迫移至 3105 |\n\n### ❌ 未验证\n\n| 功能 | 说明 |\n|------|------|\n| session-summary | 需要 /new 触发 |\n| bootstrap 注入 | 需要 /new 验证 |\n\n---\n\n**结论**：核心链路全部通畅。只剩下 router 两个 systemd 服务在后台徒劳重试，不影响使用。"}],"api":"anthropic-messages","provider":"m