{"type":"message","id":"348d49f5","parentId":"008cb2a1","timestamp":"2026-04-13T06:28:01.992Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"61342 is running but on port 3105 (since 3104 is taken by gateway). The workspace scene-classifier is NOT on 3104.\n\nLet me check what port it's actually on and fix this. The issue is that when we killed the process that was on 3104 and restarted it, the new process got 3105 because gateway took 3104 first.\n\nI need to:\n1. Kill 61342\n2. Start workspace scene-classifier (it will grab 3104 since gateway released it when it restarted)Wait, but gateway (pid 64417) is on 3104. So 61342 must be on 3105. Let me check.","thinkingSignature":"0088ac179256c6087c1afb2cc59b979f1408640ed0938d735faa3327567746d8"},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_function_v99pdyq0ec9b_1","name":"exec","arguments":{"command":"lsof -i :3105 2>/dev/null | tail -2\necho \"---\"\ncurl -s -X POST http://localhost:3105/classify -H \"Content-Type: application/json\" -d '{\"text\":\"测试\"}' 2>&1 | head -3"}}],"api":"anthropic-messages","provider":"minimax","model":"MiniMax-M2.7","usage":{"input":26024,"output":227,"cacheRead":18037,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":44288,"cost":{"input":0.007807199999999999,"output":0.0002724,"cacheRead":0.0010822199999999998,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0.00916182}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1776061674514,"responseId":"062bbfeab7e6cc062ac3b7ab638ec8df"}}
