{"type":"message","id":"4f440ff3","parentId":"504e7c40","timestamp":"2026-04-13T06:28:19.976Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"So:\n- 3104: gateway (pid 64417) - returns \"Unauthorized\" on /classify\n- 3105: workspace scene-classifier (pid 61342) - Internal Server Error\n\nBoth are broken in their own way.\n\nThe root issue: when gateway restarted, it bound to 3104 first, then when we started the workspace scene-classifier, it got 3105. But 3105 is returning Internal Server Error (the same numpy bug as before? no, the numpy bug was on 3104...).\n\nWait, but the workspace scene-classifier on 3105 - is it the old v8 version or the new workspace version? The pid 61342 was started by... let me check when it started. It was started at 14:15 according to the earlier `ps aux` output. And the workspace version was started with `bash /tmp/run_ws.sh` which runs from `/home/ai/.openclaw/workspace/skills/scene-classifier/`. \n\nBut the v8 version was also restarted multiple times. Let me check which version is on 3105. Actually, looking at the earlier port check, 61342 is the workspace version (new), but when we killed the gateway's 3104 process and restarted workspace, the gateway had already claimed 3104 so workspace got 3105 instead. Now I need to figure out why 3105 is throwing an Internal Server Error.\n\nThe v8 version was started earlier in the session around 14:04-14:05, but I've since killed and restarted several times. Let me just restart the workspace scene-classifier on 3104 and verify it's the correct version.","thinkingSignature":"d5da63504940cc70055f8c864d5671762f630bfb4536257944a9a39acfd4d12f"},{"type":"text","text":"3104 被 gateway 占了，workspace 版本挤到 3105 后返回 Internal Server Error（可能还是 numpy bug）。\n\n**修复**：重启 workspace scene-classifier，让它抢回 3104：\n"},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_function_rbo5gxv9k9wm_1","name":"exec","arguments":{"command":"kill 61342 2>/dev/null\nsleep 2\nbash /tmp/run_ws.sh\nsleep 6\nlsof -i :3104 2>/dev/null | tail -2"}}],"api":"anthropic-messages","provider":"minimax","model":"MiniMax-M2.7","usage":{"input":26322,"output":454,"cacheRead":18037,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":44813,"cost":{"input":0.0078966,"output":0.0005448,"cacheRead":0.0010822199999999998,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0.00952362}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1776061682785,"responseId":"062bbff2ed28c870272cbf4f859a84d1"}}
