{"type":"message","id":"ae644eee","parentId":"ed2ac9f5","timestamp":"2026-04-13T06:29:21.446Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"Ah I see - the print says 8080 but the actual uvicorn.run uses 3104. The log just has old messages from previous runs.\n\nThe workspace api_server.py is configured to run on 3104. But gateway is on 3104. The workspace api_server tries to bind to 3104, fails (address in use), and... does it have a fallback? It just crashes/exits. But we see process 65569 on 3105.\n\nOh wait - the run_ws.sh uses `cd /home/ai/.openclaw/workspace/skills/scene-classifier`. And the v8 version has a similar api_server.py at `/home/ai/.openclaw/v8/scene-classifier/api_server.py` (which we changed to port 3105).","thinkingSignature":"e912c7bb4ea9a6ce5d77cb3b9770056564a4510e52ee6c1d453ccffa01e886db"},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_function_ibu1l8q9ge82_1","name":"exec","arguments":{"command":"readlink -f /proc/65569/cwd 2>/dev/null\necho \"---\"\ncat /proc/65569/cmdline | tr '\\0' ' '"}}],"api":"anthropic-messages","provider":"minimax","model":"MiniMax-M2.7","usage":{"input":28952,"output":224,"cacheRead":18037,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":47213,"cost":{"input":0.0086856,"output":0.0002688,"cacheRead":0.0010822199999999998,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0.01003662}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1776061754526,"responseId":"062bc03947d73e22a474db4c88647194"}}
