{"type":"message","id":"426b06b1","parentId":"a9b81486","timestamp":"2026-04-13T06:34:35.633Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"The workspace version did start on 3108, got a request (200 OK), then was shut down when the gateway restart happened (because it was started by a shell script that got killed). Then a new instance tried to start but failed.\n\nNow only v8 (3105) is running. I need to restart the workspace version as a proper daemon that won't die on gateway restart. Let me start it again with nohup.","thinkingSignature":"30a15542a16225a5c54c1008e6eee6bf5d0703bcd7d3db68e249e74d853cbc1e"},{"type":"text","text":"workspace 版本被 gateway 重启时一并杀了。重新启动，用 nohup 保住：\n"},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_function_9ueq1v7uatnm_1","name":"exec","arguments":{"command":"nohup python3 -c \"\nimport socket\nfor port in [3108, 3109, 3110]:\n    try:\n        s = socket.socket()\n        s.bind('0.0.0.0', port)\n        s.close()\n        print(f'Using port {port}')\n        import subprocess, sys\n        subprocess.run([sys.executable, 'api_server.py'], \n            env={'PORT': str(port), **subprocess.os.environ},\n            cwd='/home/ai/.openclaw/workspace/skills/scene-classifier')\n        break\n    except OSError:\n        continue\n\" >> /tmp/sc_ws.log 2>&1 &\necho \"PID: $!\""}}],"api":"anthropic-messages","provider":"minimax","model":"MiniMax-M2.7","usage":{"input":31949,"output":275,"cacheRead":18127,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":50351,"cost":{"input":0.0095847,"output":0.00033,"cacheRead":0.0010876199999999999,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0.01100232}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1776062066978,"responseId":"062bc1729c0c835c36ebecc8305b7032"}}
