{"type":"message","id":"6a0b9bf1","parentId":"b9b5e1cb","timestamp":"2026-04-13T06:39:05.105Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"The user wants to know what each component is used for. Let me give a clear, concise explanation.","thinkingSignature":"99f96081928342172635433adeff19a6e99bdd6173aa6294fe7d8c39f99e075e"},{"type":"text","text":"## 各组件用途\n\n### 核心链路\n\n| 组件 | 作用 |\n|------|------|\n| **3104 scene-classifier** | 理解用户消息的意图场景（闲聊/任务/故障/模糊等） |\n| **3103 v8-scorer** | 评估任务复杂度，决定由谁执行（直接/步骤/子代理） |\n| **3102 gateway** | OpenClaw 主入口，所有消息都经过它 |\n\n### 记忆系统（三层）\n\n| 层 | 组件 | 作用 |\n|----|------|------|\n| 第一层 | auto-score-classify hook | 实时捕获\"有意义\"的消息，写入 ephemeral/ |\n| 第二层 | session-summary hook | session 结束时提炼，升格到 entity |\n| 第三层 | self-improving hook | /new 时把 MEMORY.md 注入新 session |\n\n### 辅助\n\n| 组件 | 用途 |\n|------|------|\n| **context-api (3101)** | 管理 session 上下文数据 |\n| **openclaw-listener (3106)** | 监听飞书消息 |\n| **cron** | 定时任务（wiki学习、记忆维护） |\n\n### 端口对应\n\n```\n3101 → context-api\n3102 → gateway 主入口（网页chat）\n3103 → v8 评分\n3108 → scene-classifier（hook调用）\n3106 → openclaw-listener\n```\n\n用户发消息 → gateway → auto-score-classify hook → 3108分类 + 3103评分 → 结果写context.json → 回复用户"}],"api":"anthropic-messages","provider":"minimax","model":"MiniMax-M2.7","usage":{"input":54,"output":344,"cacheRead":53197,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":53595,"cost":{"input":0.0000162,"output":0.0004128,"cacheRead":0.0031918199999999997,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0.00362082}},"stopReason":"stop","timestamp":1776062320993,"responseId":"062bc273c40d727463cde258bdf34e09"}}
