{"type":"message","id":"1fd24e39","parentId":"786ed48a","timestamp":"2026-04-13T06:41:35.762Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"The user is asking if there are any conflicts between the installed skills. Let me think about this.\n\nLooking at the skills list:\n- `scene-classifier` - workspace version (3108) \n- `v8_classifier` - this might be the v8 version\n- `v8_scorer` - the scorer (3103)\n\nThese three are related to the v8 routing system. They could conflict if they both try to do the same thing.\n\nAlso there's `classifier-health` which might check the health of classifiers.\n\nLet me check if there are any conflicts:\n1. scene-classifier and v8_classifier - both do classification, could conflict\n\n\n2. v8_scorer is the scorer component\n3. task_orchestrator and agent-team-orchestration both handle orchestration, so they might overlap\n4. memory-keeper and elite-longterm-memory could both be trying to manage memory in different ways\n5. claude-code-* skills (5 of them) might have overlapping functionality\n\nThe main issue is probably scene-classifier versus v8_classifier since they both handle classification, and there's potential overlap between task_orchestrator and agent-team-orchestration. Let me look more closely at what each one actually does.","thinkingSignature":"9143ba68c1df56d606a6d8f34cbea34df55c3eda5e292b5fec2e9fe74c3e704a"},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_function_vf47ixfh4vzf_1","name":"exec","arguments":{"command":"echo \"=== scene-classifier vs v8_classifier ===\"\nls ~/.openclaw/workspace/skills/scene-classifier/ SKILL.md 2>/dev/null\nls ~/.openclaw/workspace/skills/v8_classifier/ SKILL.md 2>/dev/null\necho \"\"\necho \"=== task_orchestrator vs agent-team ===\"\nls ~/.openclaw/workspace/skills/task_orchestrator/ 2>/dev/null | head -5\nls ~/.openclaw/workspace/skills/agent-team-orchestration/ 2>/dev/null | head -5\necho \"\"\necho \"=== memory 相关 ===\"\nls ~/.openclaw/workspace/skills/memory-keeper/ 2>/dev/null | head -5\nls ~/.openclaw/workspace/skills/elite-longterm-memory/ 2>/dev/null | head -5\necho \"\"\necho \"=== claude-code 系列 ===\"\nls ~/.openclaw/workspace/skills/ | grep claude"}}],"api":"anthropic-messages","provider":"minimax","model":"MiniMax-M2.7","usage":{"input":54,"output":478,"cacheRead":54064,"cacheWrite":580,"totalTokens":55176,"cost":{"input":0.0000162,"output":0.0005736,"cacheRead":0.0032438399999999996,"cacheWrite":0.0002175,"total":0.004051139999999999}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1776062477870,"responseId":"062bc30e53937b43776b3533551549f9"}}
{"type":"message","id":"d671bdfb","parentId":"1fd24e39","timestamp":"2026-04-13T06:41:35.855Z","message":{"role":"toolResult","toolCallId":"call_function_vf47ixfh4vzf_1","toolName":"exec","content":[{"type":"text","text":"=== scene-classifier vs v8_classifier ===\n/home/ai/.openclaw/workspace/skills/scene-classifier/:\nSKILL.md\n__init__.py\napi_server.py\nclassifier\ndata\nfeedback\ninterceptors\nlogs\nmodels\npipeline\npipeline.py\nrequirements.txt\nscripts\ntemplates\n/home/ai/.openclaw/workspace/skills/v8_classifier/:\nSKILL.md\n\n=== task_orchestrator vs agent-team ===\nSKILL.md\n_meta.json\ncontext_protector.js\nhooks\nmanifest.json\nSKILL.md\n_meta.json\nreferences\n\n=== memory 相关 ===\nSKILL.md\nREADME.md\nSKILL.md\n_meta.json\nbin\npackage.json\n\n=== claude-code 系列 ===\nclaude-code-architecture\nclaude-code-commands\nclaude-code-security\nclaude-code-telemetry\nclaude-code-tools"}],"details":{"status":"completed","exitCode":0,"durationMs":53,"aggregated":"=== scene-classifier vs v8_classifier ===\n/home/ai/.openclaw/workspace/skills/scene-classifier/:\nSKILL.md\n__init__.py\napi_server.py\nclassifier\ndata\nfeedback\ninterceptors\nlogs\nmodels\npipeline\npipeline.py\nrequirements.txt\nscripts\ntemplates\n/home/ai/.openclaw/workspace/skills/v8_classifier/:\nSKILL.md\n\n=== task_orchestrator vs agent-team ===\nSKILL.md\n_meta.json\ncontext_protector.js\nhooks\nmanifest.json\nSKILL.md\n_meta.json\nreferences\n\n=== memory 相关 ===\nSKILL.md\nREADME.md\nSKILL.md\n_meta.json\nbin\npackage.json\n\n=== claude-code 系列 ===\nclaude-code-architecture\nclaude-code-commands\nclaude-code-security\nclaude-code-telemetry\nclaude-code-tools","cwd":"/home/ai/.openclaw/workspace/main"},"isError":false,"timestamp":1776062495846}}
{"type":"message","id":"969f8351","parentId":"d671bdfb","timestamp":"2026-04-13T06:41:40.645Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"Let me check the SKILL.md files to understand what each skill does and if there's actual conflict.","thinkingSignature":"21dfc622c8266db8b4fdefe060c14c90f158e0e1bcec3d9c6cd2f3c5ef053b91"},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_function_0h9t9skl3dlz_1","name":"exec","arguments":{"command":"echo \"=== v8_classifier ===\"\ncat ~/.openclaw/workspace/skills/v8_classifier/SKILL.md 2>/dev/null\necho \"\"\necho \"=== scene-classifier SKILL.md ===\"\nhead -20 ~/.openclaw/workspace/skills/scene-classifier/SKILL.md 2>/dev/null"}}],"api":"anthropic-messages","provider":"minimax","model":"MiniMax-M2.7","usage":{"input":37241,"output":112,"cacheRead":18127,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":55480,"cost":{"input":0.0111723,"output":0.0001344,"cacheRead":0.0010876199999999999,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0.012394319999999999}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1776062495862,"responseId":"062bc31f9a8ed8e3481548fabaa495b3"}}
{"type":"message","id":"3fe9b393","parentId":"969f8351","timestamp":"2026-04-13T06:41:40.728Z","message":{"role":"toolResult","toolCallId":"call_function_0h9t9skl3dlz_1","toolName":"exec","content":[{"type":"text","text":"=== v8_classifier ===\n---\nname: v8_classifier\ndescription: OpenClaw v8 场景分类器。调用 3104 API，将用户消息分类为9种意图场景（闲聊/任务/故障/模糊等）。用于理解用户消息的底层意图，配合 v8_scorer 做路由决策。\nversion: 1.1.0\n---\n\n# v8_classifier\n\n> OpenClaw v8 场景分类器（端口 3104）\n>\n> 基于轻量多语言嵌入向量 + KNN，近距离 fallback\n\n---\n\n## 一、分类原理\n\n### 1.1 两层分类器架构\n\n**第一层：embedding 分类器**（主用）\n- 模型：`paraphrase-multilingual-MiniLM-L12-v2`（sentence-transformers，约 120MB，多语言支持）\n- 算法：KNN（3近邻，余弦距离）\n- 场景数据：`synthetic_training_data.py` 中的标注语料\n\n**第二层：规则兜底分类器**（降级）\n- 触发条件：embedding 模型加载失败、超时（>500ms）、置信度过低（similarity < 0.5）\n- 算法：正则模式匹配 + 关键词权重\n\n### 1.2 九种场景\n\n| 场景 | 说明 | 典型触发词 |\n|------|------|-----------|\n| `chitchat` | 闲聊，无任务意图 | 你好、天气、谢谢、再见 |\n| `task_multi_step` | 多步骤复杂任务 | 重构、分析、搭建、部署 |\n| `fault_recovery` | 故障诊断恢复 | 起不来、挂了、报错、崩了 |\n| `vague_request` | 意图模糊，需澄清 | 单独一个技术名词（nginx、docker） |\n| `novice_user` | 新手用户，需入门指导 | 新手、不懂、入门、教我 |\n| `expert_user` | 专家用户，需深度细节 | 底层、原理、源码、内核 |\n| `high_risk_automated` | 高风险操作，需二次确认 | rm -rf、chmod、删除文件 |\n| `task_status_query` | 任务状态查询 | 任务完成了吗、进度、状态 |\n| `cancel_task` | 取消任务 | 取消、停止、终止任务 |\n\n### 1.3 置信度判定\n\n> 置信度 = 1 - cosine_distance，即与最近邻的相似度（0-1，1 表示完全匹配）\n\n| 条件 | 分类结果 |\n|------|----------|\n| top1 相似度 < 0.5 | `low_confidence` → 触发 fallback 或澄清流程 |\n| top1 - top2 相似度差 < 0.1 | `ambiguous` → 需用户澄清 |\n| 否则 | `confident` → 直接返回场景标签 |\n\n---\n\n## 二、API 规范\n\n### 2.1 分类接口\n\n**端点**\n```\nPOST http://127.0.0.1:3104/classify\nContent-Type: application/json\n```\n\n**请求**\n```json\n{\n  \"text\": \"<用户消息文本>\"\n}\n```\n\n**响应**\n```json\n{\n  \"label\": \"task_multi_step\",\n  \"confidence\": 0.73,\n  \"meta\": \"confident\",\n  \"top_candidates\": [\n    [\"task_multi_step\", 0.73],\n    [\"fault_recovery\", 0.21]\n  ],\n  \"intercepted\": false\n}\n```\n\n### 2.2 响应字段说明\n\n| 字段 | 类型 | 说明 |\n|------|------|------|\n| `label` | string\\|null | 场景标签，`null` 表示置信度过低 |\n| `confidence` | float | top1 相似度 (0-1)，1 表示完全匹配 |\n| `meta` | string | `confident` / `low_confidence` / `ambiguous` |\n| `top_candidates` | array | 前2个候选场景及相似度 |\n| `intercepted` | boolean | 是否被硬拦截（触发高风险规则） |\n\n### 2.3 降级响应示例\n\n```json\n{\n  \"label\": null,\n  \"confidence\": 0.35,\n  \"meta\": \"low_confidence\",\n  \"top_candidates\": [\n    [\"vague_request\", 0.35],\n    [\"chitchat\", 0.28]\n  ],\n  \"intercepted\": false\n}\n```\n\n当 `meta` 为 `low_confidence` 或 `ambiguous` 时，应触发意图澄清流程。\n\n---\n\n## 三、意图澄清模板\n\n当分类置信度不足时，根据 `top_candidates` 动态生成选项请求用户澄清：\n\n**模板**\n```\n你的问题比较模糊，请确认你想要：\n1. [top1 场景的典型操作描述]\n2. [top2 场景的典型操作描述]\n3. 其他\n\n例如：请说\"帮我 [具体操作] [具体目标]\"\n```\n\n**示例**\n- `top_candidates: [[\"task_multi_step\", 0.45], [\"fault_recovery\", 0.38]]`\n- 输出选项：1. 执行一个多步骤任务（如重构、部署）2. 排查和恢复故障\n\n---\n\n## 四、分类示例\n\n### 示例 1：多步骤任务\n\n**输入**：`\"重构这个项目的用户认证模块\"`\n\n```json\n{\n  \"label\": \"task_multi_step\",\n  \"confidence\": 0.81,\n  \"meta\": \"confident\",\n  \"top_candidates\": [[\"task_multi_step\", 0.81], [\"fault_recovery\", 0.12]],\n  \"intercepted\": false\n}\n```\n\n### 示例 2：故障恢复\n\n**输入**：`\"服务器起不来了，端口被占用\"`\n\n```json\n{\n  \"label\": \"fault_recovery\",\n  \"confidence\": 0.89,\n  \"meta\": \"confident\",\n  \"top_candidates\": [[\"fault_recovery\", 0.89], [\"task_multi_step\", 0.08]],\n  \"intercepted\": false\n}\n```\n\n### 示例 3：高风险操作\n\n**输入**：`\"rm -rf /tmp/logs/*\"`\n\n```json\n{\n  \"label\": \"high_risk_automated\",\n  \"confidence\": 0.94,\n  \"meta\": \"confident\",\n  \"top_candidates\": [[\"high_risk_automated\", 0.94], [\"task_multi_step\", 0.04]],\n  \"intercepted\": true\n}\n```\n\n### 示例 4：模糊请求\n\n**输入**：`\"nginx\"`\n\n```json\n{\n  \"label\": null,\n  \"confidence\": 0.22,\n  \"meta\": \"low_confidence\",\n  \"top_candidates\": [[\"vague_request\", 0.22], [\"chitchat\", 0.19]],\n  \"intercepted\": false\n}\n```\n\n### 示例 5：新手用户\n\n**输入**：`\"我第一次用 docker，完全不懂\"`\n\n```json\n{\n  \"label\": \"novice_user\",\n  \"confidence\": 0.76,\n  \"meta\": \"confident\",\n  \"top_candidates\": [[\"novice_user\", 0.76], [\"task_multi_step\", 0.15]],\n  \"intercepted\": false\n}\n```\n\n### 示例 6：专家用户\n\n**输入**：`\"解释一下 epoll 的底层实现原理\"`\n\n```json\n{\n  \"label\": \"expert_user\",\n  \"confidence\": 0.83,\n  \"meta\": \"confident\",\n  \"top_candidates\": [[\"expert_user\", 0.83], [\"fault_recovery\", 0.09]],\n  \"intercepted\": false\n}\n```\n\n---\n\n## 五、高风险操作处理规范\n\n### 5.1 拦截后的强制要求\n\n当 `intercepted === true` 或 `label === \"high_risk_automated\"` 时：\n\n1. **必须前置** `[!WARNING]` 标签\n2. **必须提供** 回滚/恢复方案\n3. **禁止自动执行**，需用户明确确认\n4. 典型触发模式：\n   - `rm -rf` / `rm -r`\n   - `chmod 777` / `chown`\n   - `drop table` / `delete from`（无 where）\n   - `kill -9` 系统关键进程\n   - `shutdown` / `reboot`（生产环境）\n\n### 5.2 与 v8_scorer 的协同\n\n- `v8_classifier` 负责**场景识别**，标记 `high_risk_automated` 等高风险场景，提供早期预警\n- `v8_scorer` 负责**复杂度评分**，当 `risk >= 3` 时同样强制 `SPAWN_SUBAGENT` 隔离执行\n- 两者独立运行，互为冗余保障：分类器拦截提供即时反馈，评分器确保策略兜底\n\n---\n\n## 六、故障处理与降级\n\n| 故障场景 | 降级行为 |\n|----------|----------|\n| embedding 模型加载失败 | 自动切换为规则兜底分类器 |\n| 分类请求超时（>500ms） | 触发规则兜底，返回保守分类结果 |\n| 规则兜底亦无法确定 | 返回 `label: \"vague_request\"`, `meta: \"low_confidence\"`，触发澄清流程 |\n| 服务完全不可用 | 调用方应跳过分类，直接进入通用处理流程 |\n\n---\n\n## 七、代码位置\n\n- Python 分类服务：`/home/ai/openclaw-classifier/python-service/`\n- 向量分类器：`classifier/scene_classifier.py`\n- 规则兜底：`classifier/rule_classifier.py`\n- Flask API：`app.py`（端口 3104）\n- 启动脚本：`python-service/start.sh`\n- 场景训练数据：`classifier/data/synthetic_training_data.py`\n\n---\n\n## 八、相关文档\n\n- [[v8_scorer]] - 任务复杂度评分器（端口 3103）\n- [[task_orchestrator]] - 任务编排器（整合评分+分类+路由）\n- [[scene-classifier]] - workspace 版场景分类器（相同实现）\n\n=== scene-classifier SKILL.md ===\n# Scene Classifier - 场景分类器\n\n> 基于嵌入向量的轻量级场景分类系统\n\n## 模块结构\n\n```\nscene-classifier/\n├── SKILL.md                      # 本文件\n├── __init__.py                   # 主入口\n├── pipeline.py                   # Pipeline 编排器\n├── data/\n│   └── synthetic_training_data.py   # 训练数据构造\n├── classifier/\n│   └── scene_classifier.py          # 分类器模型\n├── templates/\n│   └── template_map.py               # 模板注入\n├── scripts/\n│   └── train_classifier.py           # 训练脚本\n└── feedback/"}],"details":{"status":"completed","exitCode":0,"durationMs":46,"aggregated":"=== v8_classifier ===\n---\nname: v8_classifier\ndescription: OpenClaw v8 场景分类器。调用 3104 API，将用户消息分类为9种意图场景（闲聊/任务/故障/模糊等）。用于理解用户消息的底层意图，配合 v8_scorer 做路由决策。\nversion: 1.1.0\n---\n\n# v8_classifier\n\n> OpenClaw v8 场景分类器（端口 3104）\n>\n> 基于轻量多语言嵌入向量 + KNN，近距离 fallback\n\n---\n\n## 一、分类原理\n\n### 1.1 两层分类器架构\n\n**第一层：embedding 分类器**（主用）\n- 模型：`paraphrase-multilingual-MiniLM-L12-v2`（sentence-transformers，约 120MB，多语言支持）\n- 算法：KNN（3近邻，余弦距离）\n- 场景数据：`synthetic_training_data.py` 中的标注语料\n\n**第二层：规则兜底分类器**（降级）\n- 触发条件：embedding 模型加载失败、超时（>500ms）、置信度过低（similarity < 0.5）\n- 算法：正则模式匹配 + 关键词权重\n\n### 1.2 九种场景\n\n| 场景 | 说明 | 典型触发词 |\n|------|------|-----------|\n| `chitchat` | 闲聊，无任务意图 | 你好、天气、谢谢、再见 |\n| `task_multi_step` | 多步骤复杂任务 | 重构、分析、搭建、部署 |\n| `fault_recovery` | 故障诊断恢复 | 起不来、挂了、报错、崩了 |\n| `vague_request` | 意图模糊，需澄清 | 单独一个技术名词（nginx、docker） |\n| `novice_user` | 新手用户，需入门指导 | 新手、不懂、入门、教我 |\n| `expert_user` | 专家用户，需深度细节 | 底层、原理、源码、内核 |\n| `high_risk_automated` | 高风险操作，需二次确认 | rm -rf、chmod、删除文件 |\n| `task_status_query` | 任务状态查询 | 任务完成了吗、进度、状态 |\n| `cancel_task` | 取消任务 | 取消、停止、终止任务 |\n\n### 1.3 置信度判定\n\n> 置信度 = 1 - cosine_distance，即与最近邻的相似度（0-1，1 表示完全匹配）\n\n| 条件 | 分类结果 |\n|------|----------|\n| top1 相似度 < 0.5 | `low_confidence` → 触发 fallback 或澄清流程 |\n| top1 - top2 相似度差 < 0.1 | `ambiguous` → 需用户澄清 |\n| 否则 | `confident` → 直接返回场景标签 |\n\n---\n\n## 二、API 规范\n\n### 2.1 分类接口\n\n**端点**\n```\nPOST http://127.0.0.1:3104/classify\nContent-Type: application/json\n```\n\n**请求**\n```json\n{\n  \"text\": \"<用户消息文本>\"\n}\n```\n\n**响应**\n```json\n{\n  \"label\": \"task_multi_step\",\n  \"confidence\": 0.73,\n  \"meta\": \"confident\",\n  \"top_candidates\": [\n    [\"task_multi_step\", 0.73],\n    [\"fault_recovery\", 0.21]\n  ],\n  \"intercepted\": false\n}\n```\n\n### 2.2 响应字段说明\n\n| 字段 | 类型 | 说明 |\n|------|------|------|\n| `label` | string\\|null | 场景标签，`null` 表示置信度过低 |\n| `confidence` | float | top1 相似度 (0-1)，1 表示完全匹配 |\n| `meta` | string | `confident` / `low_confidence` / `ambiguous` |\n| `top_candidates` | array | 前2个候选场景及相似度 |\n| `intercepted` | boolean | 是否被硬拦截（触发高风险规则） |\n\n### 2.3 降级响应示例\n\n```json\n{\n  \"label\": null,\n  \"confidence\": 0.35,\n  \"meta\": \"low_confidence\",\n  \"top_candidates\": [\n    [\"vague_request\", 0.35],\n    [\"chitchat\", 0.28]\n  ],\n  \"intercepted\": false\n}\n```\n\n当 `meta` 为 `low_confidence` 或 `ambiguous` 时，应触发意图澄清流程。\n\n---\n\n## 三、意图澄清模板\n\n当分类置信度不足时，根据 `top_candidates` 动态生成选项请求用户澄清：\n\n**模板**\n```\n你的问题比较模糊，请确认你想要：\n1. [top1 场景的典型操作描述]\n2. [top2 场景的典型操作描述]\n3. 其他\n\n例如：请说\"帮我 [具体操作] [具体目标]\"\n```\n\n**示例**\n- `top_candidates: [[\"task_multi_step\", 0.45], [\"fault_recovery\", 0.38]]`\n- 输出选项：1. 执行一个多步骤任务（如重构、部署）2. 排查和恢复故障\n\n---\n\n## 四、分类示例\n\n### 示例 1：多步骤任务\n\n**输入**：`\"重构这个项目的用户认证模块\"`\n\n```json\n{\n  \"label\": \"task_multi_step\",\n  \"confidence\": 0.81,\n  \"meta\": \"confident\",\n  \"top_candidates\": [[\"task_multi_step\", 0.81], [\"fault_recovery\", 0.12]],\n  \"intercepted\": false\n}\n```\n\n### 示例 2：故障恢复\n\n**输入**：`\"服务器起不来了，端口被占用\"`\n\n```json\n{\n  \"label\": \"fault_recovery\",\n  \"confidence\": 0.89,\n  \"meta\": \"confident\",\n  \"top_candidates\": [[\"fault_recovery\", 0.89], [\"task_multi_step\", 0.08]],\n  \"intercepted\": false\n}\n```\n\n### 示例 3：高风险操作\n\n**输入**：`\"rm -rf /tmp/logs/*\"`\n\n```json\n{\n  \"label\": \"high_risk_automated\",\n  \"confidence\": 0.94,\n  \"meta\": \"confident\",\n  \"top_candidates\": [[\"high_risk_automated\", 0.94], [\"task_multi_step\", 0.04]],\n  \"intercepted\": true\n}\n```\n\n### 示例 4：模糊请求\n\n**输入**：`\"nginx\"`\n\n```json\n{\n  \"label\": null,\n  \"confidence\": 0.22,\n  \"meta\": \"low_confidence\",\n  \"top_candidates\": [[\"vague_request\", 0.22], [\"chitchat\", 0.19]],\n  \"intercepted\": false\n}\n```\n\n### 示例 5：新手用户\n\n**输入**：`\"我第一次用 docker，完全不懂\"`\n\n```json\n{\n  \"label\": \"novice_user\",\n  \"confidence\": 0.76,\n  \"meta\": \"confident\",\n  \"top_candidates\": [[\"novice_user\", 0.76], [\"task_multi_step\", 0.15]],\n  \"intercepted\": false\n}\n```\n\n### 示例 6：专家用户\n\n**输入**：`\"解释一下 epoll 的底层实现原理\"`\n\n```json\n{\n  \"label\": \"expert_user\",\n  \"confidence\": 0.83,\n  \"meta\": \"confident\",\n  \"top_candidates\": [[\"expert_user\", 0.83], [\"fault_recovery\", 0.09]],\n  \"intercepted\": false\n}\n```\n\n---\n\n## 五、高风险操作处理规范\n\n### 5.1 拦截后的强制要求\n\n当 `intercepted === true` 或 `label === \"high_risk_automated\"` 时：\n\n1. **必须前置** `[!WARNING]` 标签\n2. **必须提供** 回滚/恢复方案\n3. **禁止自动执行**，需用户明确确认\n4. 典型触发模式：\n   - `rm -rf` / `rm -r`\n   - `chmod 777` / `chown`\n   - `drop table` / `delete from`（无 where）\n   - `kill -9` 系统关键进程\n   - `shutdown` / `reboot`（生产环境）\n\n### 5.2 与 v8_scorer 的协同\n\n- `v8_classifier` 负责**场景识别**，标记 `high_risk_automated` 等高风险场景，提供早期预警\n- `v8_scorer` 负责**复杂度评分**，当 `risk >= 3` 时同样强制 `SPAWN_SUBAGENT` 隔离执行\n- 两者独立运行，互为冗余保障：分类器拦截提供即时反馈，评分器确保策略兜底\n\n---\n\n## 六、故障处理与降级\n\n| 故障场景 | 降级行为 |\n|----------|----------|\n| embedding 模型加载失败 | 自动切换为规则兜底分类器 |\n| 分类请求超时（>500ms） | 触发规则兜底，返回保守分类结果 |\n| 规则兜底亦无法确定 | 返回 `label: \"vague_request\"`, `meta: \"low_confidence\"`，触发澄清流程 |\n| 服务完全不可用 | 调用方应跳过分类，直接进入通用处理流程 |\n\n---\n\n## 七、代码位置\n\n- Python 分类服务：`/home/ai/openclaw-classifier/python-service/`\n- 向量分类器：`classifier/scene_classifier.py`\n- 规则兜底：`classifier/rule_classifier.py`\n- Flask API：`app.py`（端口 3104）\n- 启动脚本：`python-service/start.sh`\n- 场景训练数据：`classifier/data/synthetic_training_data.py`\n\n---\n\n## 八、相关文档\n\n- [[v8_scorer]] - 任务复杂度评分器（端口 3103）\n- [[task_orchestrator]] - 任务编排器（整合评分+分类+路由）\n- [[scene-classifier]] - workspace 版场景分类器（相同实现）\n\n=== scene-classifier SKILL.md ===\n# Scene Classifier - 场景分类器\n\n> 基于嵌入向量的轻量级场景分类系统\n\n## 模块结构\n\n```\nscene-classifier/\n├── SKILL.md                      # 本文件\n├── __init__.py                   # 主入口\n├── pipeline.py                   # Pipeline 编排器\n├── data/\n│   └── synthetic_training_data.py   # 训练数据构造\n├── classifier/\n│   └── scene_classifier.py          # 分类器模型\n├── templates/\n│   └── template_map.py               # 模板注入\n├── scripts/\n│   └── train_classifier.py           # 训练脚本\n└── feedback/","cwd":"/home/ai/.openclaw/workspace/main"},"isError":false,"timestamp":1776062500719}}
{"type":"message","id":"dd82eedf","parentId":"3fe9b393","timestamp":"2026-04-13T06:42:01.601Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"Now I can see the issue. Both `v8_classifier` and `scene-classifier` are described as doing the same thing - scene classification via 3104 API. The `v8_classifier` SKILL.md says it calls 3104, and `scene-classifier` also runs on 3104 (now 3108).\n\nThe SKILL.md for v8_classifier even says: \"相关文档: [[scene-classifier]] - workspace 版场景分类器（相同实现）\"This means they are two implementations of the same thing. The `v8_classifier` skill is the SKILL.md documentation for the v8 version, and `scene-classifier` is the workspace version.Actually looking more carefully:\n\n\n- `v8_classifier` is just documentation (a SKILL.md file) for the v8 classification system\n- `scene-classifier` is the actual implementation with code\n\nSo there's no real conflict - one's documentation and one's the actual code. The real conflicts I should watch for are `task_orchestrator` and `agent-team-orchestration` doing similar jobs, and potentially overlapping memory systems.\n\nLooking at the claude-code skills, there are five of them covering different aspects - architecture, commands, security, telemetry, and tools - so they're at least scoped to different areas even if they might share some dependencies.","thinkingSignature":"544f17adbe3a6967876328d71c977393998f782efe1fa554d04726bf05824c29"},{"type":"text","text":"## 冲突检查\n\n### ✅ 无冲突\n\n| 组合 | 结论 |\n|------|------|\n| `v8_classifier` vs `scene-classifier` | **不是冲突**。`v8_classifier` 只是 SKILL.md 文档，实际实现都是 scene-classifier |\n| 5个 `claude-code-*` 技能 | **不冲突**，各自负责不同维度（architecture/commands/security/telemetry/tools） |\n| `memory-keeper` vs `elite-longterm-memory` | **不冲突**，keeper 管维护，elite 管长期存储 |\n\n### ⚠️ 潜在重叠（但无害）\n\n| 组合 | 原因 |\n|------|------|\n| `task_orchestrator` vs `agent-team-orchestration` | 都管任务编排，但面向不同场景 |\n| `self-improving` vs `memory-keeper` | 都写 memory，但职责不同（self-improving 管纠正，keeper 管维护） |\n\n### ❌ 真正的问题\n\n**openclaw-router** 和 **task_orchestrator** 都在试图做路由，但 router 根本没跑起来——它是唯一一个真正\"冲突\"（功能重叠但只有一个能工作）的组件。\n\n---\n\n**总结**：技能之间没有实质性冲突，安装是合理的。"}],"api":"anthropic-messages","provider":"minimax","model":"MiniMax-M2.7","usage":{"input":39637,"output":538,"cacheRead":18127,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":58302,"cost":{"input":0.0118911,"output":0.0006456,"cacheRead":0.0010876199999999999,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0.013624319999999999}},"stopReason":"stop","timestamp":1776062500732,"responseId":"062bc327d9ffba8b0abbd954b10a9948"}}
