{"type":"message","id":"21b3c5aa","parentId":"e2c915b6","timestamp":"2026-04-13T06:42:54.982Z","message":{"role":"user","content":[{"type":"text","text":"Sender (untrusted metadata):\n```json\n{\n  \"label\": \"openclaw-control-ui\",\n  \"id\": \"openclaw-control-ui\"\n}\n```\n\n[Mon 2026-04-13 14:42 GMT+8] openclaw-router 和 task_orchestrator他俩有什么用"}],"timestamp":1776062574972}}
{"type":"message","id":"257a5877","parentId":"21b3c5aa","timestamp":"2026-04-13T06:43:14.056Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"The user is asking what openclaw-router and task_orchestrator do. Let me give a concise answer based on what I know from the context.\n\n- openclaw-router: was supposed to be an intelligent routing layer, but it never got deployed (missing @isaced/ai-router module)\n- task_orchestrator: a skill in workspace that manages task execution with hooks","thinkingSignature":"9ae37f4ba3f2f67495d7cd992f17e1b4a632543af25ff0b4c39c5c79035e6cb5"},{"type":"text","text":"## 两者对比\n\n| | openclaw-router | task_orchestrator |\n|--|-----------------|-------------------|\n| **定位** | 独立路由服务（二进制） | workspace 技能（SKILL.md） |\n| **功能** | AI 路由——理解用户意图后路由到合适模型/Agent | 任务编排——管理多步骤任务的执行、状态、失败恢复 |\n| **状态** | ❌ 从未成功部署（缺核心依赖） | ✅ 在用 |\n| **架构** | 独立进程，gateway 外层 | gateway 内联，通过 hook 协作 |\n\n---\n\n## openclaw-router（设计意图）\n\n```\n用户消息 → router → 路由到 CLAUDE/CLAUDE-CODE/本地模型等\n```\n\n理论上：gateway 收到消息 → 发给 router → router 判断走哪个模型/Agent → 返回结果\n\n**实际上**：跑不起来，缺 `@isaced/ai-router` 这个 npm 包。\n\n---\n\n## task_orchestrator（实际在用）\n\n```\n用户消息 → gateway → 3104分类 + 3103评分 → 根据策略执行\n                                          ↓\n                                    DIRECT（简单任务）\n                                    SPAWN_SUBAGENT（复杂任务）\n                                    STEP（多步骤）\n```\n\n它不是一个独立服务，而是**散落在各处的一段逻辑**：\n- hook 里做分类/评分（`auto-score-classify`）\n- scorer 里算复杂度\n- gateway 里根据评分决定是否 spawn subagent\n\n---\n\n## 结论\n\n**task_orchestrator 是实际在跑的任务编排逻辑。**\n\n**openclaw-router** 本来想做一个更上层的路由层（路由到不同 Agent/模型），但一直没能部署，**其实可以忽略它**——它不影响当前核心链路。"}],"api":"anthropic-messages","provider":"minimax","model":"MiniMax-M2.7","usage":{"input":54,"output":433,"cacheRead":54662,"cacheWrite":3092,"totalTokens":58241,"cost":{"input":0.0000162,"output":0.0005195999999999999,"cacheRead":0.00327972,"cacheWrite":0.0011595,"total":0.00497502}},"stopReason":"stop","timestamp":1776062574999,"responseId":"062bc36f6083e79c0b687d5868d00bfb"}}
