{"type":"message","id":"6780ba84","parentId":"c9625d59","timestamp":"2026-04-13T06:48:17.640Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"Good. Now let me also update the session summary to reflect the current state more accurately.","thinkingSignature":"a7dd2c7b6149fcf5553638ae4cc744a7f6b215d583041e9f60b11e14848b2899"},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_function_9j3qpsln932m_1","name":"exec","arguments":{"command":"cat >> ~/.openclaw/workspace/memory/2026-04-13-14-session.md << 'ENDOFFILE'\n\n---\n\n## 补充：/new 后操作步骤（已写入 MEMORY.md）\n\n在 MEMORY.md 末尾新增了完整链路说明，包括：\n1. 读取历史文件\n2. 提炼 ephemeral\n3. 验证记忆闭环\n4. 确认框架状态\n\n同时更新了 SOUL.md 启动检查规则，强制首次回复前读取 MEMORY.md。\n\n## 已知未验证项\n- session-summary hook\n- bootstrap 注入\n- ephemeral → entity 升格\nENDOFFILE\necho \"done\""}}],"api":"anthropic-messages","provider":"minimax","model":"MiniMax-M2.7","usage":{"input":41531,"output":178,"cacheRead":18127,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":59836,"cost":{"input":0.0124593,"output":0.0002136,"cacheRead":0.0010876199999999999,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0.013760519999999998}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1776062890408,"responseId":"062bc4aacafbff9e35499d346d9a3510"}}
