{"type":"message","id":"e8fb3249","parentId":"a1b3bfa3","timestamp":"2026-04-13T06:48:23.509Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"Good. Now let me verify MEMORY.md was actually written to.","thinkingSignature":"77fb61b85eef9d2c3903569663bbbcc2044305bb69c2fb8e1321393bea3ea1b3"},{"type":"text","text":"**已写入 MEMORY.md**。下次 /new 后，新 session 的我会在 SOUL.md 启动检查时读 MEMORY.md，看到：\n\n```\n/new 后记忆链路（完整步骤）\n├── 第一步：读取历史文件\n├── 第二步：提炼 ephemeral（如有）\n├── 第三步：验证记忆闭环\n└── 第四步：确认框架状态\n```\n\n即便 bootstrap 注入失效、hook 链路断裂，这条规则也会强制执行。这是记忆链路的最后一道人工防线。"}],"api":"anthropic-messages","provider":"minimax","model":"MiniMax-M2.7","usage":{"input":41726,"output":118,"cacheRead":18127,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":59971,"cost":{"input":0.012517799999999999,"output":0.0001416,"cacheRead":0.0010876199999999999,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0.013747019999999999}},"stopReason":"stop","timestamp":1776062897739,"responseId":"062bc4b1ec8019dd90052df3176bcd1e"}}
